1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, prošle godine, školske godine imali smo razmišljanje ovak malo o vjerovanju. Ove godine krećemo sa razmišljanjem o dogmanskim konstitucijama II. Vatikasov koncila, a to znači evo, nekako najmodernijim dokumentima koje nas neki način potiču, obvezuju hrabre, da uđemo dublje u tu avanturu s Bogom.

2
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerovanje je sažetak Biblije i dovoljno je to moliti nakon sa srcem, zapravo već si ušao u cijelu onda Bibliju. Danas, evo, krećemo sa dokumentom Dei Verbum i ovim tekstom iz druge poslanice Solunjanima koja je ovako vrlo znakovita rečenica.

3
00:00:50,000 --> 00:01:06,700
[SPEAKER_01] Stoga braćo, ali ćemo namast i sestre, evo isto dakle svi koji smo ovdje zajedno, čvrsto stojte i držate se predaja u kojima ste poučeni bilo našom riječju, bilo pismom.

4
00:01:08,079 --> 00:01:14,120
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, taj tekst vrlo zgodno spaja Božju riječ i ljudsku predaju.

5
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:18,640
[SPEAKER_01] Kako to izgleda ljudska predaja? To je ova debela knjižurina, dakle.

6
00:01:20,079 --> 00:01:28,939
[SPEAKER_01] Piše, zbirka sažetaka, pazite, znači, ne pa sažetci su ovu sažecili, vjerovanja, definicija, izjava o vjeri i čudoređu.

7
00:01:28,939 --> 00:01:37,560
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, toka je jedna zgodna knjiga napisana kronološkim redom po vladavini pojedinih papa.

8
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:50,140
[SPEAKER_01] Kako su ti pape donali sve neke dokumente koje su danas za nas katolike obvezatne, pogotovo ako se radi o dogmama, njih moramo prihvatiti i o njima razmišljati.

9
00:01:50,140 --> 00:01:55,680
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto ćemo malo iz ove debela knjižurina nešto vidjeti, ali nećemo se čija, dakle bi bilo to preopštino.

10
00:01:57,519 --> 00:02:08,939
[SPEAKER_01] Ima to onaj dobar vic na račun protestanata, kada je Martin Luther započeo svoju reformu, onda je napisao poznatu rečenicu ili izjavu

11
00:02:08,939 --> 00:02:18,719
[SPEAKER_01] sola scriptura, sola gracia, sola fidei. Samo pismo, samo vjera i samo dostatije milost, ništa više.

12
00:02:18,719 --> 00:02:24,439
[SPEAKER_01] A onda katolici šaljivo odgovaraju, to su prve rečenice koje u Bibliji ne pišu.

13
00:02:24,979 --> 00:02:30,879
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, samo sola scriptura, samo pismo. Prva rečenica koje u Bibliji ne piše, dakle, on se na to poziva.

14
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ovako malo ošaljivo. Mi katolici imamo predaju, imamo pismo.

15
00:02:36,659 --> 00:02:43,379
[SPEAKER_01] Nastanak pisma. U Starom Zavijetu Bog je polako pripremao.

16
00:02:43,379 --> 00:02:49,020
[SPEAKER_01] Svaka ljudska perioda ima svoju milost.

17
00:02:49,020 --> 00:02:52,919
[SPEAKER_01] Stari Zavijet je vršio pripravu za dolazak Isusa.

18
00:02:54,719 --> 00:02:57,639
[SPEAKER_01] U pojedinim vremenima nije bilo pojedinih njiga iz Biblije.

19
00:02:57,639 --> 00:03:03,939
[SPEAKER_01] Početci te pismenosti imamo negdje za vreme Mojsija.

20
00:03:03,939 --> 00:03:08,139
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, on je 1500 godina prije Hrista.

21
00:03:08,139 --> 00:03:12,139
[SPEAKER_01] Nekakvi tragovi, bliž da vam pravima tisući toj godini.

22
00:03:12,139 --> 00:03:14,300
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogi tnike da još nisu napisane.

23
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:19,960
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ti ljudi u to vrijeme imaju vrlo mali obsek Božje riječi.

24
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:23,979
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto umaglovito možemo reći.

25
00:03:23,979 --> 00:03:29,039
[SPEAKER_01] Što idemo dalje, pogotovo od kralja Davida, onda imamo sve više te pisane riječi.

26
00:03:29,039 --> 00:03:32,060
[SPEAKER_01] Biblija se sve više nadopunjava.

27
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:34,620
[SPEAKER_01] Sve više knjiga ima.

28
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:44,020
[SPEAKER_01] To je na fakultetu jedna cijela znanost proučavanja nastanka Biblije kroz nekakvih 1350 godina njezine povijesti.

29
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:49,699
[SPEAKER_01] Od prvih zapisa pa sve više i onda do Novog Zavjeta.

30
00:03:49,699 --> 00:03:56,960
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je pomalo preko svojih proroka pokušavao ljude nadahnuti za čitanje pisma.

31
00:03:57,300 --> 00:04:03,620
[SPEAKER_01] Onda nam dolaze vrijeme Isusa, koje je zapravo ispunjenje svih starozavjetnih proroštava.

32
00:04:03,620 --> 00:04:07,919
[SPEAKER_01] Sve ono što je napisano, u njemu se kompletno stvaruje.

33
00:04:07,919 --> 00:04:14,340
[SPEAKER_01] Od mjesta rođenja Betlehema ćemo govoriti prorok Mihej, tamo ne ide šestostoljeće prije Krista,

34
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:21,100
[SPEAKER_01] do razpeća na križu, psalam recimo 22, Bože moj, Bože moj, zašto si me ostavio,

35
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:25,480
[SPEAKER_01] koje Isus moli na križu, tisuću godina prije njega napisan,

36
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:30,800
[SPEAKER_01] ili prorok Izaija koji do slovce opisuje njegovu smrt, osam stoljeća prije,

37
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:35,620
[SPEAKER_01] i tako redom, 260 citata ostvaruje se u Isusu.

38
00:04:35,620 --> 00:04:42,079
[SPEAKER_01] I kršćani ga prepoznaju kao Mesiju koji je najavljen u Starom Zavjetu

39
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:47,959
[SPEAKER_01] i onda do kraja očitovan u svoje vrijeme.

40
00:04:47,959 --> 00:04:49,879
[SPEAKER_01] To je taj dio.

41
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:56,019
[SPEAKER_01] Onda imamo 20 godina od Isusove smrti, do tamo negdje 50. godine,

42
00:04:56,019 --> 00:05:01,060
[SPEAKER_01] kada nastane upravo ova postavnica Solunjana, ima prva i druga Pavlova,

43
00:05:01,060 --> 00:05:05,519
[SPEAKER_01] one se smatraju najstari ispis i star Novog Zavjeta,

44
00:05:05,519 --> 00:05:08,459
[SPEAKER_01] negdje oko 50. godine po Isusu Hrstu.

45
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:12,339
[SPEAKER_01] Prvi, znači, ispis je prva i druga postavnica Solunjanima.

46
00:05:12,339 --> 00:05:16,339
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, danas imamo nekako najstari ispis o čemu razmatramo.

47
00:05:16,339 --> 00:05:20,040
[SPEAKER_01] 20 godina kršćani nemaju ništa.

48
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:22,319
[SPEAKER_01] Nemaju evanđelje.

49
00:05:22,319 --> 00:05:25,399
[SPEAKER_01] Nemaju postavnica Novog Zavjeta.

50
00:05:25,399 --> 00:05:26,120
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa nemaju.

51
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:31,399
[SPEAKER_01] Imaju samo stari zavjet i ostvarenje tog zavjeta o Isusu.

52
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:36,120
[SPEAKER_01] Jer Pavlova, kao što sigurno znate, u postavnici Solunjanima piše

53
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:38,579
[SPEAKER_01] da će uskoro doći smak svijeta.

54
00:05:38,579 --> 00:05:43,819
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je zamišljen tom idejom, pa sad bučio da je smak svijeta blizu,

55
00:05:43,819 --> 00:05:45,279
[SPEAKER_01] čemu se opterećivati.

56
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:49,160
[SPEAKER_01] A od tog vremena, prošla je 2000. godina, još nije smak svijet bio.

57
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:51,079
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, Pavlova bi se tada objavio.

58
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:54,480
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da treba gledati tu postavnicu Solunjanima u tom kontekstu

59
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:58,600
[SPEAKER_01] da je pisana iz te vizije kraj svijeta.

60
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,060
[SPEAKER_01] Pa šta će ti sad onda nešto više.

61
00:06:00,060 --> 00:06:02,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kako su apostoli počeli umirati

62
00:06:02,079 --> 00:06:04,220
[SPEAKER_01] ili, boje rečino, bili ubijani?

63
00:06:04,220 --> 00:06:07,160
[SPEAKER_01] Od sredo se poto se nešto zapiše.

64
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:10,459
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je Pavlova zapisao prvu i drugu postavnicu Solunjanima

65
00:06:10,459 --> 00:06:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] kao najstariji spis Novog Zavjeta.

66
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:15,420
[SPEAKER_01] Na početku su evanđelje, budu dijela apostolska.

67
00:06:15,420 --> 00:06:16,939
[SPEAKER_01] Pa Pavlova je postavnica.

68
00:06:16,939 --> 00:06:21,300
[SPEAKER_01] One su podijeljene tematski, dakle, ili po autorima u Bibliji,

69
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:24,480
[SPEAKER_01] a ne po kronologiji nastanka.

70
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:27,040
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ne do knjige po redu u Bibliji,

71
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:29,620
[SPEAKER_01] kako su pisane, nego po nekakvim tematikama

72
00:06:29,620 --> 00:06:30,459
[SPEAKER_01] koje su složene.

73
00:06:30,459 --> 00:06:32,939
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je oposlenica Solunjanja na polovici,

74
00:06:32,939 --> 00:06:35,439
[SPEAKER_01] a zapravo je prva knjiga Novog Zavjeta

75
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,779
[SPEAKER_01] koja je kao tako napisana.

76
00:06:36,779 --> 00:06:40,779
[SPEAKER_01] I onda su kršćani skupljali te knjige,

77
00:06:40,779 --> 00:06:43,480
[SPEAKER_01] najznačajniji je Svjeti Jeronim,

78
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:47,480
[SPEAKER_01] koji je preveo sa grčkoga i hebrejskoga,

79
00:06:48,860 --> 00:06:51,639
[SPEAKER_01] Bibliju je tada narodni jezik.

80
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:53,459
[SPEAKER_01] To je velika stvar.

81
00:06:53,459 --> 00:06:57,839
[SPEAKER_01] Crkve je trebalo 1900. godina dosvati

82
00:06:57,839 --> 00:06:59,939
[SPEAKER_01] da je narodni jezik jako bitan.

83
00:06:59,939 --> 00:07:03,899
[SPEAKER_01] A to je već, jer on je napravio svoje vrijeme.

84
00:07:03,899 --> 00:07:06,759
[SPEAKER_01] Preveo je da će Bibliju na latinski.

85
00:07:06,759 --> 00:07:09,899
[SPEAKER_01] Tada, živući jezik koji su ljudi govorili,

86
00:07:09,899 --> 00:07:11,160
[SPEAKER_01] koji je Puk govorio,

87
00:07:12,079 --> 00:07:13,920
[SPEAKER_01] učeni ljudi govorili su grčkim jezikom,

88
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:18,500
[SPEAKER_01] a obični rimljani govorili su latinskim jezikom.

89
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:21,920
[SPEAKER_01] I na taj jezik je Jeronim preveo Bibliju.

90
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:24,740
[SPEAKER_01] I u nju stavio taj popis Svjetih knjiga,

91
00:07:24,740 --> 00:07:26,600
[SPEAKER_01] koje mi i danas koristimo.

92
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,860
[SPEAKER_01] To je dan čemljenje peto stoljeće kršćanstva.

93
00:07:28,860 --> 00:07:33,120
[SPEAKER_01] A onda se vode silne rasprave.

94
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:35,980
[SPEAKER_01] Da li su sve knjige ili nisu na tom popisu?

95
00:07:35,980 --> 00:07:41,160
[SPEAKER_01] Tako idemo skroz do tridenta,

96
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:45,579
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem se naglašava taj jedan cijeli popis,

97
00:07:45,579 --> 00:07:47,220
[SPEAKER_01] u ovoj debeloj knjižurini,

98
00:07:47,220 --> 00:07:50,899
[SPEAKER_01] to je taj cijeli popis,

99
00:07:50,899 --> 00:07:53,339
[SPEAKER_01] gdje se želim naglasiti

100
00:07:53,339 --> 00:07:56,240
[SPEAKER_01] kako se vode rasprave

101
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:58,800
[SPEAKER_01] oko sljedećih knjiga.

102
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,959
[SPEAKER_01] U vrijeme održavanja Saboranje,

103
00:08:00,959 --> 00:08:07,639
[SPEAKER_01] 3. tijskoga, to je 1545. do 63. godine,

104
00:08:07,639 --> 00:08:09,399
[SPEAKER_01] u velikim fazama se on odvijao

105
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:11,120
[SPEAKER_01] na razlih mjestima političke situacije,

106
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:11,680
[SPEAKER_01] sto čuda.

107
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:14,420
[SPEAKER_01] Znači u to vrijeme, 16. stoljeća,

108
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:18,720
[SPEAKER_01] raspravljalo se da li su sljedeće knjige kanonske.

109
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:22,519
[SPEAKER_01] A to znači Tobija, Judita,

110
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:24,860
[SPEAKER_01] Mudre izreke, Sirak,

111
00:08:24,860 --> 00:08:27,620
[SPEAKER_01] prva i druga Makabejcima, Hebrejima,

112
00:08:27,620 --> 00:08:29,399
[SPEAKER_01] druga Petrova, Jakovljeva,

113
00:08:29,959 --> 00:08:33,559
[SPEAKER_01] druga i treća Ivanova, Judina i Otkrivenje.

114
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:35,039
[SPEAKER_01] I određenja Danjela.

115
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:38,200
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, 90. knjiga iz Biblije

116
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:40,720
[SPEAKER_01] je u 16. stoljeću još sporno

117
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] da li su od Boga nadahnute.

118
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:46,360
[SPEAKER_01] Treba pratiti jedan povijesni kontekst događanja

119
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,279
[SPEAKER_01] da vidimo.

120
00:08:47,279 --> 00:08:49,500
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je na četvrtoj sjednici,

121
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:52,139
[SPEAKER_01] 8. travnja 1546.

122
00:08:52,940 --> 00:08:56,279
[SPEAKER_01] konačno definiran taj popis koji imamo danas u Bibliji.

123
00:08:56,279 --> 00:09:01,100
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, evo, Sabor je mislio da tom dekretu treba predodati i popis knjiga

124
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:04,580
[SPEAKER_01] kako se kod nekoga ne bi mogla pojaviti dvojba

125
00:09:04,580 --> 00:09:07,299
[SPEAKER_01] koje su to knjige koje Sabor prihvaća.

126
00:09:07,299 --> 00:09:09,100
[SPEAKER_01] To su niže navedene.

127
00:09:09,179 --> 00:09:13,340
[SPEAKER_01] I sad nabraja cijeli popis knjiga koji imamo danas iz Biblije.

128
00:09:13,340 --> 00:09:16,279
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, tek 1546. godine

129
00:09:16,279 --> 00:09:19,899
[SPEAKER_01] crkva definira točan popis knjiga koji imamo u Bibliji.

130
00:09:19,899 --> 00:09:21,820
[SPEAKER_01] Vidite kak je to dugačka povijest.

131
00:09:21,820 --> 00:09:25,740
[SPEAKER_01] Prije Krista i do našeg vremena.

132
00:09:25,740 --> 00:09:28,759
[SPEAKER_01] U to vrijeme, dakle, nastaje tiskarski stroj,

133
00:09:28,759 --> 00:09:35,019
[SPEAKER_01] Gutenberg, pa je Biblija dobila mogućnost da se širi.

134
00:09:35,019 --> 00:09:37,340
[SPEAKER_01] Prva tiska na stvari je upravo Biblija.

135
00:09:37,340 --> 00:09:38,840
[SPEAKER_01] To je vrlo zanimljivo.

136
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:42,080
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, od svih izdanja krećemo sa Biblijom.

137
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:45,419
[SPEAKER_01] I od tada se Biblija štampa u milijunskim nakladama

138
00:09:45,419 --> 00:09:46,940
[SPEAKER_01] čirom svijeta.

139
00:09:46,940 --> 00:09:50,980
[SPEAKER_01] Dijeli se, poklanja se, kupuje se viš kako ko ima.

140
00:09:50,980 --> 00:09:53,679
[SPEAKER_01] I mi smo privilegirana generacija

141
00:09:53,679 --> 00:09:57,480
[SPEAKER_01] koja ima čast čitati Bibliju.

142
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:59,940
[SPEAKER_01] To je velika milost.

143
00:09:59,940 --> 00:10:01,480
[SPEAKER_01] To je naše vrijeme.

144
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] I zato mi je jako drago kad vidim da mnogi od vas čitate Bibliju,

145
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:08,279
[SPEAKER_01] pocrtavate, valite si neke tekste, svaki na svoj način,

146
00:10:08,279 --> 00:10:13,679
[SPEAKER_01] proučava tu Božju riječ, što je znak da smo dobro shvatili

147
00:10:13,679 --> 00:10:15,580
[SPEAKER_01] trenutak u kojem se nalazimo.

148
00:10:15,580 --> 00:10:22,379
[SPEAKER_01] Zato crkva ima riječ Božju, a ima i tradiciju.

149
00:10:22,379 --> 00:10:24,919
[SPEAKER_01] Valjda to sve zajedno spojiti.

150
00:10:24,919 --> 00:10:28,720
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, danas ćemo nekako pokušati po ovoj Pavlovoj preporuci

151
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:33,240
[SPEAKER_01] da sve budemo povučeni riječju ili pismom.

152
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:37,379
[SPEAKER_01] Znači jednom predajom ili pismom Božjom riječju.

153
00:10:37,379 --> 00:10:41,840
[SPEAKER_01] Sve to zajedno povučava nas ljude na Božjem putu.

154
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:44,039
[SPEAKER_01] Pa evo, malo ćemo pokušati vidjeti onda taj dokument,

155
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:45,220
[SPEAKER_01] Dei Verbum.

156
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:48,639
[SPEAKER_01] Podijeli smo ga nekako, to bi se vjavljavao, na dva dijela.

157
00:10:48,639 --> 00:10:52,600
[SPEAKER_01] Prvi dio, ovako započinje dokument,

158
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:56,620
[SPEAKER_01] pa je to naziv Dei Verbum, znači po latinskom,

159
00:10:56,620 --> 00:11:03,059
[SPEAKER_01] Božju riječ sa strahu poštovanjem slušajući i vjerno je razglašajući.

160
00:11:03,059 --> 00:11:05,600
[SPEAKER_01] Slušati Božju riječ.

161
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:08,600
[SPEAKER_01] Budući da je ovo dogmatska definicija,

162
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:10,960
[SPEAKER_01] dogme su kratko sažete,

163
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:14,440
[SPEAKER_01] pa treba svaku riječ dobro analizirati što piše.

164
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:17,159
[SPEAKER_01] Znači Božju riječ treba dobro slušati.

165
00:11:17,159 --> 00:11:21,519
[SPEAKER_01] To činimo, kad smo svaki dan na svetu emisiju,

166
00:11:21,519 --> 00:11:23,740
[SPEAKER_01] hvala Bogu, većina od vas je na svetu emisiju svaki dan,

167
00:11:23,740 --> 00:11:26,179
[SPEAKER_01] i slušate Božju riječ.

168
00:11:26,179 --> 00:11:29,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ona ima moć učiniti nešto u našem životu.

169
00:11:29,980 --> 00:11:33,820
[SPEAKER_01] Dugačka je lista ljudi od svetog Agustina,

170
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:35,059
[SPEAKER_01] recimo najpoznatija,

171
00:11:35,059 --> 00:11:38,179
[SPEAKER_01] iz Rimljanima 13.13, pa do naših dana,

172
00:11:38,179 --> 00:11:41,240
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je Božja riječ mijenjala ljudske živote.

173
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:44,200
[SPEAKER_01] Kad su se sreli sa tom riječju,

174
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:47,120
[SPEAKER_01] život se promijenio iz temelja.

175
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:51,120
[SPEAKER_01] Od temelje misli koje imamo na svim susretima,

176
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,440
[SPEAKER_01] da nas Bog jako voli,

177
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:54,220
[SPEAKER_01] da je svaki čovjek voljen,

178
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:56,519
[SPEAKER_01] tu se mnogi ljudi rasplaću,

179
00:11:56,519 --> 00:11:58,019
[SPEAKER_01] dožive emocije ili slično,

180
00:11:58,019 --> 00:11:59,940
[SPEAKER_01] jer je jako to gane u dušu,

181
00:11:59,940 --> 00:12:02,899
[SPEAKER_01] pa do neznam kakvi sve nespoznaja

182
00:12:02,899 --> 00:12:05,100
[SPEAKER_01] koje Bog čini u našem životu.

183
00:12:05,100 --> 00:12:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] Sve to po Božju riječi.

184
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:11,299
[SPEAKER_01] Ili kad neko ima dar sporošla spoznanja,

185
00:12:11,299 --> 00:12:13,279
[SPEAKER_01] pa ti Bog preko njega progovara,

186
00:12:13,279 --> 00:12:15,100
[SPEAKER_01] ali opet ti govori istinu.

187
00:12:15,100 --> 00:12:17,720
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto ti kaže značajno.

188
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:20,519
[SPEAKER_01] Što mijenja tvoj život, naravno, na bolje.

189
00:12:21,659 --> 00:12:24,279
[SPEAKER_01] To su načine kakve Bog komunicira s nama.

190
00:12:24,279 --> 00:12:26,279
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže posrednica Hebrejima,

191
00:12:26,279 --> 00:12:30,840
[SPEAKER_01] da je Bog više puta i na više načina ljudima govorio.

192
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:33,259
[SPEAKER_01] Konačno ove dane progovore nam u sinu.

193
00:12:34,100 --> 00:12:36,360
[SPEAKER_01] Bog želi s nama razgovarati.

194
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:38,480
[SPEAKER_01] To je njegovo temelje obilježje.

195
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:41,759
[SPEAKER_01] Mi možemo toga bježati ili to prihvaćati.

196
00:12:41,759 --> 00:12:45,440
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ja se nadam da većina od vas prihvaća taj razgovor s Bogom

197
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:48,600
[SPEAKER_01] preko Biblije gdje nalazimo tu svoju utjehu.

198
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:50,879
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je ovo, znači, sa strahom poštovanjem,

199
00:12:50,879 --> 00:12:52,240
[SPEAKER_01] slušajući tu riječ.

200
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:55,320
[SPEAKER_01] To je riječ Božja.

201
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:59,620
[SPEAKER_01] Nije isto da li ti govori Bog

202
00:12:59,620 --> 00:13:02,340
[SPEAKER_01] ili netko ovako običan čovjek.

203
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:07,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ako to uspoređujemo sa, recimo, nekom drugom religijom,

204
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:09,820
[SPEAKER_01] a ima jedna koja kaže

205
00:13:09,820 --> 00:13:11,740
[SPEAKER_01] proklet, onaj koji kaže

206
00:13:11,740 --> 00:13:13,440
[SPEAKER_01] Isus Krist, Bog i spasitelj.

207
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:15,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ima je takva jedna religija na svijetu.

208
00:13:15,860 --> 00:13:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] Onda se pitaš

209
00:13:18,039 --> 00:13:20,100
[SPEAKER_01] ko se li govori istinu?

210
00:13:20,100 --> 00:13:24,259
[SPEAKER_01] Ova riječ Božja kaže da si po Isusu spašen,

211
00:13:24,259 --> 00:13:27,399
[SPEAKER_01] a ta religija kaže da si proklet

212
00:13:27,399 --> 00:13:29,340
[SPEAKER_01] ako kažeš da je Isus spasitelj.

213
00:13:29,340 --> 00:13:31,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ne može Bog jedno drugo govoriti.

214
00:13:31,639 --> 00:13:32,759
[SPEAKER_01] Bio bi to smiješan Bog.

215
00:13:33,740 --> 00:13:35,259
[SPEAKER_01] Najprije kaže u Stavnom zavijetu

216
00:13:35,259 --> 00:13:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] evo, Isus je Mesija,

217
00:13:38,500 --> 00:13:41,419
[SPEAKER_01] a onda nakon šest tođe se taj Bog

218
00:13:41,419 --> 00:13:43,259
[SPEAKER_01] predomisli i kaže, ne, ne, tu sam se zaburi,

219
00:13:43,259 --> 00:13:44,100
[SPEAKER_01] Isus nije Mesija.

220
00:13:44,100 --> 00:13:47,559
[SPEAKER_01] To je dosta teško tako prihvatiti takvu Boga.

221
00:13:47,559 --> 00:13:49,940
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je dostajan uvijek, uvijek isto govori.

222
00:13:49,940 --> 00:13:51,179
[SPEAKER_01] I nekada,

223
00:13:51,179 --> 00:13:52,659
[SPEAKER_01] i u vreme Isusa i danas.

224
00:13:53,659 --> 00:13:55,500
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je naglasak Božju riječ.

225
00:13:55,500 --> 00:13:57,419
[SPEAKER_01] Ne je bilo kakvu riječ.

226
00:13:57,419 --> 00:13:59,220
[SPEAKER_01] Slušajući.

227
00:13:59,220 --> 00:14:02,340
[SPEAKER_01] Mi u Biblii prepozvamo da je to Božja riječ.

228
00:14:03,340 --> 00:14:06,080
[SPEAKER_01] koju moramo što više usvojiti.

229
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:10,259
[SPEAKER_01] Neko je dobro pamti, neki ljudi znaju citate silne.

230
00:14:10,259 --> 00:14:13,899
[SPEAKER_01] E onda bilo koji način doći u kontakt s tom riječju.

231
00:14:13,899 --> 00:14:16,299
[SPEAKER_01] Prvenstveno je slušajući.

232
00:14:18,700 --> 00:14:21,399
[SPEAKER_01] A onda je, nekako drugima razglašujemo.

233
00:14:21,399 --> 00:14:23,139
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, sami smo u dušenitom riječju,

234
00:14:23,139 --> 00:14:25,419
[SPEAKER_01] onda nas je toliko dijede na srcu,

235
00:14:25,419 --> 00:14:27,240
[SPEAKER_01] da želimo i drugima prenijeti.

236
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,679
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je nastavak ovog teksta.

237
00:14:28,679 --> 00:14:33,059
[SPEAKER_01] Sveti sabor snijedi svetog Ivana, apostola ili njegove poslanici,

238
00:14:33,059 --> 00:14:36,200
[SPEAKER_01] na vještovan život vječni,

239
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:39,399
[SPEAKER_01] koji bijaše kod oca i nama se pokazu.

240
00:14:39,399 --> 00:14:40,799
[SPEAKER_01] Govorimo o to životu vječnome.

241
00:14:40,799 --> 00:14:44,860
[SPEAKER_01] Sva duhovnost je usmjerena prema ocu.

242
00:14:44,860 --> 00:14:46,980
[SPEAKER_01] Biblija, sve što radimo.

243
00:14:47,820 --> 00:14:50,159
[SPEAKER_01] Navještamo vam ono što smo vidjeli i čuli.

244
00:14:50,159 --> 00:14:52,940
[SPEAKER_01] Da i vi imate zajedništvo s nama,

245
00:14:52,940 --> 00:14:55,960
[SPEAKER_01] te naše zajedništvo bude s ocem i sa sinom,

246
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:57,120
[SPEAKER_01] njegovim Isusom Hristom.

247
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:59,120
[SPEAKER_01] Što smo vidjeli i čuli,

248
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:01,539
[SPEAKER_01] da imamo zajedništvo s njime.

249
00:15:01,539 --> 00:15:02,840
[SPEAKER_01] To vam navještamo.

250
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Biti svjestan da po Božoj riječi imaš zajedništvo s Bogom.

251
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:08,620
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kućeš ljepše.

252
00:15:08,620 --> 00:15:11,279
[SPEAKER_01] Direktni kontakt s Bogom.

253
00:15:11,279 --> 00:15:14,080
[SPEAKER_01] Bogom koji čini čudesa i danas,

254
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] znamenja, evo mi često vidimo ovdje čudesa u našoj zajednici,

255
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,340
[SPEAKER_01] na bilo koji način,

256
00:15:18,340 --> 00:15:19,500
[SPEAKER_01] jer ste govorili o živom Bogu.

257
00:15:19,500 --> 00:15:20,580
[SPEAKER_01] Njegovite živi Bog,

258
00:15:20,580 --> 00:15:22,120
[SPEAKER_01] tamo su čudesa.

259
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:25,019
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje je nekakvi ljudski Bog,

260
00:15:25,019 --> 00:15:25,840
[SPEAKER_01] tamo je nešto drugo.

261
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:27,580
[SPEAKER_01] Nadam sam čuo jedan bisaj,

262
00:15:27,580 --> 00:15:28,620
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, koji bi se jako svidio,

263
00:15:28,620 --> 00:15:30,320
[SPEAKER_01] ali u kontrasmjeru,

264
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:32,580
[SPEAKER_01] tumači jedan svečenik,

265
00:15:32,580 --> 00:15:33,379
[SPEAKER_01] kako je Biblija,

266
00:15:33,379 --> 00:15:36,139
[SPEAKER_01] samo znanstvena knjiga.

267
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:39,059
[SPEAKER_01] I moraš što bolje znanstveno proučiti,

268
00:15:39,059 --> 00:15:39,759
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je koji zared,

269
00:15:39,759 --> 00:15:40,500
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je koja točka,

270
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:42,139
[SPEAKER_01] koliko ima koji riječi.

271
00:15:42,139 --> 00:15:43,440
[SPEAKER_01] E to je bitno za Bibliju.

272
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:45,240
[SPEAKER_01] Da Biblija donosi život,

273
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:46,679
[SPEAKER_01] to je nekako ispustio.

274
00:15:46,679 --> 00:15:47,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ba, ili bi još malo čudno,

275
00:15:47,820 --> 00:15:49,039
[SPEAKER_01] ali tako je bilo rečeno,

276
00:15:49,039 --> 00:15:51,480
[SPEAKER_01] je nekako da je Biblija samo znanstvena knjiga.

277
00:15:52,340 --> 00:15:53,759
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo je tako proučavati,

278
00:15:53,759 --> 00:15:55,179
[SPEAKER_01] ali ona prvenstveno donosi život.

279
00:15:55,179 --> 00:15:57,340
[SPEAKER_01] To je njezina oznaka.

280
00:15:57,340 --> 00:16:00,399
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, pa to je prvi dio dokumenta.

281
00:16:00,399 --> 00:16:01,559
[SPEAKER_01] Drugi dio je

282
00:16:01,559 --> 00:16:04,840
[SPEAKER_01] svoj koncil,

283
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:06,340
[SPEAKER_01] idući stopama Trinitinskog

284
00:16:06,340 --> 00:16:07,820
[SPEAKER_01] i prvog Vatikarskog koncila.

285
00:16:07,820 --> 00:16:09,620
[SPEAKER_01] Malo prvi sam pročito ovaj dekret

286
00:16:09,620 --> 00:16:11,480
[SPEAKER_01] o ustanovljenju

287
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,919
[SPEAKER_01] popisa svetih knjiga

288
00:16:12,919 --> 00:16:14,879
[SPEAKER_01] iz 1546. godine.

289
00:16:14,879 --> 00:16:16,559
[SPEAKER_01] Na istom tragu je

290
00:16:16,559 --> 00:16:18,059
[SPEAKER_01] i prvi Vatikarski koncil,

291
00:16:18,059 --> 00:16:20,100
[SPEAKER_01] koji nije završen,

292
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:21,720
[SPEAKER_01] ali je uspio izglasati

293
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:23,940
[SPEAKER_01] dokument o Božjoj riječi

294
00:16:23,940 --> 00:16:26,100
[SPEAKER_01] i o papinoj nepogrešivosti.

295
00:16:26,100 --> 00:16:27,899
[SPEAKER_01] Jer je Garibaldi umoširao u Rim,

296
00:16:27,899 --> 00:16:30,080
[SPEAKER_01] pa je prvi Vatikarski sabor

297
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:31,100
[SPEAKER_01] nasilno prekinut

298
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:32,080
[SPEAKER_01] i nije dalje dovršen,

299
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:35,120
[SPEAKER_01] ali je uspio govoriti o Božjoj riječi.

300
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:37,259
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, također ćemo to moći vidjeti.

301
00:16:37,259 --> 00:16:39,100
[SPEAKER_01] Onda, kan izjeti pravi nauku

302
00:16:39,100 --> 00:16:39,940
[SPEAKER_01] u Božjoj objavi,

303
00:16:39,940 --> 00:16:41,440
[SPEAKER_01] njezinu prenošenju,

304
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:42,600
[SPEAKER_01] kako bi sav svijest,

305
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:44,399
[SPEAKER_01] slušajući navještaj spasljenja,

306
00:16:44,399 --> 00:16:46,620
[SPEAKER_01] uzvjerovao, u vjeri se nadao

307
00:16:46,620 --> 00:16:47,980
[SPEAKER_01] i u nadi ljubio.

308
00:16:47,980 --> 00:16:50,200
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to je prva točka ovoga dokumenta,

309
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:51,740
[SPEAKER_01] gde i vjeru,

310
00:16:51,740 --> 00:16:52,720
[SPEAKER_01] jako je značajno,

311
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:54,980
[SPEAKER_01] gotovo svaka riječ nešto svoje kaže,

312
00:16:54,980 --> 00:16:56,980
[SPEAKER_01] pa je, evo, malo smo ovako

313
00:16:56,980 --> 00:16:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] pokušali da bolje analizirati.

314
00:16:58,539 --> 00:16:59,919
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, možemo dalje.

315
00:16:59,919 --> 00:17:02,740
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to je prvi Vatikarski koncil,

316
00:17:02,740 --> 00:17:03,659
[SPEAKER_01] što kaže o objavi.

317
00:17:04,660 --> 00:17:07,180
[SPEAKER_01] Tko kaže da Boga jedinog i pravog,

318
00:17:07,180 --> 00:17:08,279
[SPEAKER_01] našeg spasa gospodana,

319
00:17:08,279 --> 00:17:10,660
[SPEAKER_01] nije moguće sigurno spoznati

320
00:17:10,660 --> 00:17:12,920
[SPEAKER_01] naravnim svijetlom ljudskog razuma,

321
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:14,720
[SPEAKER_01] preko onoga što je učinjeno,

322
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:16,519
[SPEAKER_01] neka bude kažnjen anatemom,

323
00:17:16,519 --> 00:17:17,940
[SPEAKER_01] znači jednim prokledstvom.

324
00:17:17,940 --> 00:17:19,500
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, nije više katolik,

325
00:17:19,500 --> 00:17:20,660
[SPEAKER_01] nije član crkve.

326
00:17:20,660 --> 00:17:23,240
[SPEAKER_01] Tko kaže da se ne može dogoditi

327
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:25,380
[SPEAKER_01] ili da ne koristi da čovek

328
00:17:25,380 --> 00:17:26,779
[SPEAKER_01] u objavi bude poučen,

329
00:17:26,779 --> 00:17:28,099
[SPEAKER_01] o Bogu i štovanju

330
00:17:28,099 --> 00:17:29,420
[SPEAKER_01] kojemu treba iskazivati,

331
00:17:29,420 --> 00:17:31,720
[SPEAKER_01] neka bude kažnjen anatemom.

332
00:17:31,819 --> 00:17:32,839
[SPEAKER_01] Prvi Vatreski koncil,

333
00:17:32,839 --> 00:17:35,359
[SPEAKER_01] to je zadnji koncil koji koristi

334
00:17:35,359 --> 00:17:37,059
[SPEAKER_01] tu definiciju anatema.

335
00:17:37,059 --> 00:17:39,099
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ako ne prihvaćaš dogmu,

336
00:17:39,099 --> 00:17:41,779
[SPEAKER_01] ako ne prihvaća ovdje sve što piše,

337
00:17:41,779 --> 00:17:44,259
[SPEAKER_01] je pod prokledstvom,

338
00:17:44,259 --> 00:17:46,180
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, ne ba da niče uvri na jel.

339
00:17:46,180 --> 00:17:48,819
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, nećemo sve to proučavati danas,

340
00:17:48,819 --> 00:17:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali nijak hoćemo,

341
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:52,500
[SPEAKER_01] da vidimo, upoznamo svoju vjeru,

342
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:54,359
[SPEAKER_01] pa da budemo što bolji katolici.

343
00:17:54,359 --> 00:17:56,420
[SPEAKER_01] To nam je nekako glavni cilj.

344
00:17:56,420 --> 00:17:59,420
[SPEAKER_01] Malo prije smo imali na sliku Isusa na...

345
00:17:59,420 --> 00:18:01,740
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, Isus,

346
00:18:01,819 --> 00:18:02,660
[SPEAKER_01] naravno na obali,

347
00:18:02,660 --> 00:18:05,220
[SPEAKER_01] ponaje pjesmi Kriz na žalu,

348
00:18:05,220 --> 00:18:08,259
[SPEAKER_01] a mreža biće riječ Božja prava.

349
00:18:08,259 --> 00:18:10,240
[SPEAKER_01] Mreža u kojoj se ljudi hvataju

350
00:18:10,240 --> 00:18:11,920
[SPEAKER_01] je riječ Božja.

351
00:18:11,920 --> 00:18:14,980
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je moramo prvi sami dobro poznavati

352
00:18:14,980 --> 00:18:17,319
[SPEAKER_01] i drugima govoriti.

353
00:18:17,319 --> 00:18:19,420
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, Bog ti piše to,

354
00:18:19,420 --> 00:18:20,640
[SPEAKER_01] Bog ti žele to poručiti,

355
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:21,680
[SPEAKER_01] Bog te ljubi,

356
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:22,859
[SPEAKER_01] Bog ima plan s tobom,

357
00:18:22,859 --> 00:18:24,880
[SPEAKER_01] bilo koja već nadahnuće dobiješ,

358
00:18:24,880 --> 00:18:26,480
[SPEAKER_01] ali u Božjoj riječi.

359
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:28,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ne na nekim ljudskim umovima.

360
00:18:28,420 --> 00:18:30,140
[SPEAKER_01] Isus je koristio tu Božju riječ,

361
00:18:30,140 --> 00:18:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] tam je bio Bog

362
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:33,900
[SPEAKER_01] i na taj način je hvatao ljude.

363
00:18:33,900 --> 00:18:36,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znamo kak je prve apostole uhvatio,

364
00:18:36,539 --> 00:18:38,339
[SPEAKER_01] bacite mreža,

365
00:18:38,339 --> 00:18:38,980
[SPEAKER_01] oni basiše,

366
00:18:38,980 --> 00:18:39,980
[SPEAKER_01] pođeše za njim.

367
00:18:39,980 --> 00:18:41,799
[SPEAKER_01] Veliko čudo se dogodilo

368
00:18:41,799 --> 00:18:44,099
[SPEAKER_01] upravo po toj Božjoj riječi

369
00:18:44,099 --> 00:18:45,160
[SPEAKER_01] koja je doliku snažna.

370
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:47,019
[SPEAKER_01] To je isto i danas što Bog čini.

371
00:18:47,019 --> 00:18:50,039
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, zamoljuću Dari,

372
00:18:50,039 --> 00:18:50,839
[SPEAKER_01] Dari da malo ustani,

373
00:18:50,839 --> 00:18:51,599
[SPEAKER_01] da vidite svi.

374
00:18:51,599 --> 00:18:53,140
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, imamo danas

375
00:18:53,140 --> 00:18:54,539
[SPEAKER_01] u našoj zajednicima Kapucina,

376
00:18:54,539 --> 00:18:56,279
[SPEAKER_01] kojeg je Bog uhvatio

377
00:18:56,279 --> 00:18:57,400
[SPEAKER_01] u Kapucinski red.

378
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:59,099
[SPEAKER_01] Dari je član naše zajednice,

379
00:18:59,099 --> 00:19:00,220
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje je od prije,

380
00:19:00,220 --> 00:19:02,660
[SPEAKER_01] pa je Boga dotaknuo

381
00:19:02,660 --> 00:19:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] i ovih dana imao je zavijete,

382
00:19:04,960 --> 00:19:05,920
[SPEAKER_01] prve redovničke

383
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:08,740
[SPEAKER_01] za Kapucinskog pripravnika.

384
00:19:08,740 --> 00:19:10,779
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, tako Bog hvata.

385
00:19:10,779 --> 00:19:11,619
[SPEAKER_01] Možete ga poslije pitati

386
00:19:11,619 --> 00:19:12,819
[SPEAKER_01] kako ga je to Bog uhvatio,

387
00:19:12,819 --> 00:19:14,819
[SPEAKER_01] na koji način u svoju mrežu.

388
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:16,680
[SPEAKER_01] Mrežu duhovnog poziva,

389
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:18,720
[SPEAKER_01] pa daj Boža da se još nekog hvati

390
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:19,299
[SPEAKER_01] u tu mrežu,

391
00:19:19,299 --> 00:19:20,259
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, na taj način,

392
00:19:20,259 --> 00:19:22,240
[SPEAKER_01] da bude puno dobrih ulova,

393
00:19:22,240 --> 00:19:24,319
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, na ovu našoj zajednici.

394
00:19:24,319 --> 00:19:26,420
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, tako Isus hvata.

395
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:28,279
[SPEAKER_01] Nekada i danas uvijek isto

396
00:19:28,279 --> 00:19:30,079
[SPEAKER_01] po riječi svoje,

397
00:19:30,079 --> 00:19:31,400
[SPEAKER_01] pa je nam jako bitno

398
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:32,299
[SPEAKER_01] tu riječ što bolje

399
00:19:32,299 --> 00:19:33,119
[SPEAKER_01] onda upozna.

400
00:19:33,119 --> 00:19:35,220
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to je to.

401
00:19:35,220 --> 00:19:35,799
[SPEAKER_01] Sad idemo

402
00:19:35,799 --> 00:19:38,539
[SPEAKER_01] sa točkama dokumenta.

403
00:19:38,539 --> 00:19:40,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ovaj ćemo dokumenta podijeliti

404
00:19:40,859 --> 00:19:42,660
[SPEAKER_01] u dva susreta.

405
00:19:42,660 --> 00:19:44,380
[SPEAKER_01] Danas svako bi čenite u Bibliji,

406
00:19:45,019 --> 00:19:45,859
[SPEAKER_01] a sljedeći put,

407
00:19:45,859 --> 00:19:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] kad će biti moja tema,

408
00:19:47,380 --> 00:19:49,759
[SPEAKER_01] onda će biti o nastavku

409
00:19:49,759 --> 00:19:50,740
[SPEAKER_01] tog dokumenta,

410
00:19:50,740 --> 00:19:51,759
[SPEAKER_01] Dei verbum,

411
00:19:51,759 --> 00:19:53,460
[SPEAKER_01] znači dogmose konstitucije

412
00:19:53,460 --> 00:19:55,839
[SPEAKER_01] o Božoj riječi,

413
00:19:55,839 --> 00:19:57,680
[SPEAKER_01] koju valja dobro šitavati.

414
00:19:57,680 --> 00:20:00,160
[SPEAKER_01] Narav i predmet objave.

415
00:20:00,980 --> 00:20:02,579
[SPEAKER_01] Što to Bog objavljuje?

416
00:20:02,579 --> 00:20:06,140
[SPEAKER_01] Iz Ivana ukevanđelja

417
00:20:06,140 --> 00:20:08,319
[SPEAKER_01] da je Bog ljubav,

418
00:20:08,319 --> 00:20:10,160
[SPEAKER_01] to je temeljna istina.

419
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:13,019
[SPEAKER_01] Da je Bog tako ljubio svijet,

420
00:20:13,019 --> 00:20:15,640
[SPEAKER_01] to je dao svoga sina rođenca,

421
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:17,579
[SPEAKER_01] da nijedan koji u njega vjeruje

422
00:20:17,579 --> 00:20:18,380
[SPEAKER_01] ne propadne,

423
00:20:18,380 --> 00:20:20,059
[SPEAKER_01] nego da ima život vječni.

424
00:20:20,940 --> 00:20:21,880
[SPEAKER_01] To je Božja nakana.

425
00:20:21,880 --> 00:20:25,059
[SPEAKER_01] Danas, evo baš je mojo krasno razmišljanje

426
00:20:25,059 --> 00:20:26,759
[SPEAKER_01] vezano za blagdan

427
00:20:26,759 --> 00:20:28,680
[SPEAKER_01] uzvišenja svijetog križa.

428
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:31,140
[SPEAKER_01] Križ koji je uzdignut.

429
00:20:31,140 --> 00:20:34,440
[SPEAKER_01] Sražetak cijele Bože ljubavi.

430
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:38,259
[SPEAKER_01] Na klavare imaš dvije osobe,

431
00:20:38,259 --> 00:20:39,240
[SPEAKER_01] dva križa još.

432
00:20:39,240 --> 00:20:41,680
[SPEAKER_01] Lijevog i desnog razbojnika.

433
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:44,519
[SPEAKER_01] Moraš se svrsta dječeš.

434
00:20:44,519 --> 00:20:46,299
[SPEAKER_01] Oćeš na ljevu stranu,

435
00:20:46,299 --> 00:20:47,339
[SPEAKER_01] pa Isusa vrijeđati,

436
00:20:47,339 --> 00:20:48,240
[SPEAKER_01] psovati,

437
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:49,720
[SPEAKER_01] spasi sebe i nas,

438
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:50,640
[SPEAKER_01] pa ti si Mesija,

439
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:51,900
[SPEAKER_01] pa da učini nešto.

440
00:20:51,900 --> 00:20:54,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ili ćeš sa desnim razbojnikom reći

441
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:56,819
[SPEAKER_01] smiluj se gospode na meni,

442
00:20:56,819 --> 00:20:58,400
[SPEAKER_01] sjeti mi se kad uđeš u svoje kraljestvo.

443
00:20:59,259 --> 00:21:00,740
[SPEAKER_01] Danas ćeš biti sa mnom u raju.

444
00:21:00,740 --> 00:21:03,359
[SPEAKER_01] Danas možeš biti s Bogom u raju.

445
00:21:03,359 --> 00:21:06,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ako prihvatiš njegov nauk o križu.

446
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:09,940
[SPEAKER_01] To je tako kratki govor,

447
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:11,440
[SPEAKER_01] a tako snažan.

448
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:15,160
[SPEAKER_01] U postanici Korinčanima

449
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:18,119
[SPEAKER_01] imamo više govora o tome,

450
00:21:18,119 --> 00:21:23,099
[SPEAKER_01] gdje Pavo naglašava važnost svoga križa.

451
00:21:23,099 --> 00:21:25,940
[SPEAKER_01] Sada ćemo, evo, to mislim malo pročijati.

452
00:21:28,839 --> 00:21:39,579
[SPEAKER_00] U istinu,

453
00:21:39,579 --> 00:21:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] besjeda o križu ludosti onima koji propadaju,

454
00:21:43,460 --> 00:21:46,799
[SPEAKER_00] a nama spašenicima sila je Božja.

455
00:21:46,799 --> 00:21:48,660
[SPEAKER_00] Ta pisano je,

456
00:21:48,660 --> 00:21:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] upropasti ću mudrost mudrih

457
00:21:51,119 --> 00:21:52,900
[SPEAKER_00] i odbacit ću umnost umnih.

458
00:21:53,660 --> 00:21:54,440
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je mudrac?

459
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:56,259
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je književnik?

460
00:21:56,259 --> 00:21:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je istraživač ovoga svijeta?

461
00:21:58,960 --> 00:22:01,579
[SPEAKER_00] Zar ne izludi Bog mudrost svijeta?

462
00:22:01,579 --> 00:22:03,400
[SPEAKER_00] Doista,

463
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:08,400
[SPEAKER_00] kad svijetu mudrosti Božjoj Boga ne upozna mudrošću,

464
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:13,200
[SPEAKER_00] svidjelo se Bogu ludošću propovjedanja spasiti vjernike.

465
00:22:14,039 --> 00:22:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] Jer i židovi znake ištu i grci mudro straže.

466
00:22:17,539 --> 00:22:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] A mi propovjedamo Krista raspetoga,

467
00:22:20,900 --> 00:22:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] židovima sablazan,

468
00:22:22,940 --> 00:22:24,559
[SPEAKER_00] poganima ludost,

469
00:22:24,559 --> 00:22:28,440
[SPEAKER_00] pozvanima pak i židovima i grcima

470
00:22:28,440 --> 00:22:32,319
[SPEAKER_00] Krista Božju snagu i Božju mudrost.

471
00:22:33,319 --> 00:22:35,779
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ludo Božje mudrije je od ljudi

472
00:22:35,779 --> 00:22:38,799
[SPEAKER_00] i slabo Božje jače je od ljudi.

473
00:22:38,799 --> 00:22:41,240
[SPEAKER_00] Da gledajte, braćo, sebe,

474
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:42,519
[SPEAKER_00] pozvane,

475
00:22:42,519 --> 00:22:44,640
[SPEAKER_00] nema mnogo mudrih po tijelu,

476
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:46,680
[SPEAKER_00] nema mnogo snažnih,

477
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] nema mnogo plemenitih,

478
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] nego lude svijeta izabra Bog da posrami mudre

479
00:22:52,059 --> 00:22:55,480
[SPEAKER_00] i slabe svijeta izabra Bog da posrami jake

480
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:59,559
[SPEAKER_00] i neplemenite svijeta prezrene izabra Bog

481
00:22:59,559 --> 00:23:03,140
[SPEAKER_00] i ono što nije, da uništi ono što jest,

482
00:23:03,140 --> 00:23:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] da se nijedan smrtnik ne bi hvalio pred Bogom.

483
00:23:06,420 --> 00:23:09,900
[SPEAKER_00] Od njega je da vi jeste u Kristu Isusu,

484
00:23:09,900 --> 00:23:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] koji nama posta mudrost od Boga

485
00:23:12,420 --> 00:23:16,299
[SPEAKER_00] i pravednost i posvećenje i otkupljenje.

486
00:23:16,299 --> 00:23:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] Da bude kako je pisano,

487
00:23:18,579 --> 00:23:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] tko se hvali, u Gospodu neka se hvali.

488
00:23:22,619 --> 00:23:27,759
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, besede o križu,

489
00:23:28,599 --> 00:23:31,119
[SPEAKER_01] Prva Korinčanima 1.18.25,

490
00:23:31,119 --> 00:23:33,359
[SPEAKER_01] to je temeljni govor koji crkva koristi,

491
00:23:33,359 --> 00:23:36,299
[SPEAKER_01] zato je kada misjonari idu po svijetu,

492
00:23:36,299 --> 00:23:37,799
[SPEAKER_01] nose križ.

493
00:23:37,799 --> 00:23:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] Najednostavnije.

494
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:41,420
[SPEAKER_01] I onda tu mače ljudima,

495
00:23:41,420 --> 00:23:43,640
[SPEAKER_01] evo, to ti Bog učini, to ko te Bog ljubi.

496
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:46,779
[SPEAKER_01] Zažetak svih govora je upravo križ.

497
00:23:46,779 --> 00:23:51,240
[SPEAKER_01] Ili Prva Korinčanima 2.1.5,

498
00:23:51,240 --> 00:23:53,519
[SPEAKER_01] gdje se govori o,

499
00:23:53,519 --> 00:23:56,099
[SPEAKER_01] želimo znati samo Krista raspetoga.

500
00:23:56,599 --> 00:23:59,480
[SPEAKER_01] Pavla ništa ne zanima drugo nego jedino Krista raspeti,

501
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:03,400
[SPEAKER_01] koji opet zažetak ovo govora o čemu smo malo prije razmišljali.

502
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:07,319
[SPEAKER_01] U poslanici Kološanima 2.8,

503
00:24:07,319 --> 00:24:11,640
[SPEAKER_01] Pavlo će reći da ne žele slušati ljudske predaje,

504
00:24:11,640 --> 00:24:13,660
[SPEAKER_01] nego samo Krista.

505
00:24:13,660 --> 00:24:15,180
[SPEAKER_01] Samo on ga zanima.

506
00:24:15,599 --> 00:24:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to bih dobiti nekako i naš tražetak i naše razmišljanje o Bogu.

507
00:24:20,079 --> 00:24:23,160
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je ovaj narav i predmet objave.

508
00:24:23,440 --> 00:24:27,859
[SPEAKER_01] je Bog koji ljubi, koji se objavlja u čovjeku riječima i znakovima.

509
00:24:27,859 --> 00:24:30,299
[SPEAKER_01] Krist je središte tog događaja.

510
00:24:31,039 --> 00:24:34,579
[SPEAKER_01] i kaže, Bog, evo, to ti je sve rješenje.

511
00:24:34,579 --> 00:24:39,240
[SPEAKER_01] Kada se tamo događana objava Božja,

512
00:24:39,240 --> 00:24:42,779
[SPEAKER_01] onda otac kaže, ovo je sin moj ljubljeni,

513
00:24:42,779 --> 00:24:44,400
[SPEAKER_01] njega slušajte.

514
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:46,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa drugo, samo njega.

515
00:24:46,920 --> 00:24:50,299
[SPEAKER_01] To bi je rješenje svih vaših životnih problema i teškoća.

516
00:24:50,299 --> 00:24:54,319
[SPEAKER_01] Gledamo na Isusa, a ne na probleme i teškoće.

517
00:24:54,319 --> 00:24:57,680
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, vezano za tu narav i sve ostalo.

518
00:24:57,680 --> 00:24:59,940
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo jednu krasnu knjižicu

519
00:24:59,940 --> 00:25:02,220
[SPEAKER_01] Znanost božanske ljubavi.

520
00:25:02,220 --> 00:25:05,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ovako, vrlo mala knjižica, ali vrlo znakovita.

521
00:25:05,319 --> 00:25:09,519
[SPEAKER_01] Napisao je naš pokojni profesor, bibličar Bonaventura Duda,

522
00:25:09,519 --> 00:25:14,940
[SPEAKER_01] koji je na temelju male Terezije napisao ovu knjižicu

523
00:25:14,940 --> 00:25:16,640
[SPEAKER_01] i to za njezina dva događaja.

524
00:25:16,740 --> 00:25:18,759
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo, njezina stovtu godišnjicu rođenja,

525
00:25:18,759 --> 00:25:21,539
[SPEAKER_01] 1973.

526
00:25:21,539 --> 00:25:27,819
[SPEAKER_01] I za njezina godišnjicu smrti, stovtu godišnjicu,

527
00:25:27,819 --> 00:25:29,660
[SPEAKER_01] dva zgodna predavanja.

528
00:25:29,660 --> 00:25:34,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo, vezano za Terezijino rođenje,

529
00:25:34,019 --> 00:25:35,599
[SPEAKER_01] nastovio je ovako.

530
00:25:35,599 --> 00:25:39,900
[SPEAKER_01] Otkriće Biblije u duhovnosti male Terezije.

531
00:25:39,900 --> 00:25:42,539
[SPEAKER_01] Kako je mala Terezija otkrila Bibliju?

532
00:25:42,539 --> 00:25:46,420
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, pa, to je bilo njegov poznato predavanje.

533
00:25:46,559 --> 00:25:50,660
[SPEAKER_01] koje je održao 73. godine u prigodnih te stvote godišnjice,

534
00:25:50,660 --> 00:25:52,579
[SPEAKER_01] pa sad donosi neke primjere.

535
00:25:52,579 --> 00:25:55,740
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, u to vrijeme, to je kraj 19. stoljeća,

536
00:25:55,740 --> 00:26:00,660
[SPEAKER_01] Biblija se ne čita, pa čak niti u samostanima.

537
00:26:01,920 --> 00:26:04,859
[SPEAKER_01] iako je štampana, iako je ima nebožno velikoj količini,

538
00:26:04,859 --> 00:26:08,839
[SPEAKER_01] ali Biblija je štivo koje niti redovnice ne čitaju.

539
00:26:08,839 --> 00:26:11,440
[SPEAKER_01] 500 godina, pazite.

540
00:26:12,980 --> 00:26:15,079
[SPEAKER_01] čak neki način izabranjena knjiga.

541
00:26:15,079 --> 00:26:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] Nema je to očinjati, to je komplicirano štivo.

542
00:26:18,619 --> 00:26:20,680
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, upravo u tom kontekstu,

543
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:23,859
[SPEAKER_01] Patre Duda objašnjava kako je mala Terezija

544
00:26:23,859 --> 00:26:26,059
[SPEAKER_01] otkrila Bibliju.

545
00:26:28,299 --> 00:26:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njoj su govorili da je Bog jako dalek,

546
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:34,599
[SPEAKER_01] strok, kažnjava,

547
00:26:34,599 --> 00:26:36,900
[SPEAKER_01] sve nešto suprotno Bibliji.

548
00:26:36,900 --> 00:26:39,119
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je bilo odgajana.

549
00:26:39,119 --> 00:26:41,619
[SPEAKER_01] A onda je,

550
00:26:41,619 --> 00:26:46,160
[SPEAKER_01] buđa da je ona potekla iz jedne svete obitelji,

551
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:49,619
[SPEAKER_01] njezini su roditelji danas sveci katoličke crkve,

552
00:26:49,619 --> 00:26:51,579
[SPEAKER_01] znači, vrlo zanimljava obitelj,

553
00:26:51,579 --> 00:26:54,200
[SPEAKER_01] roditelji sveti, ona svetica,

554
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:56,460
[SPEAKER_01] sve njezine sestre išle u samostan,

555
00:26:56,460 --> 00:27:00,039
[SPEAKER_01] po redu, dakle, ovako vrlo na duho na obitelj.

556
00:27:00,039 --> 00:27:01,759
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ovdje u zajednici kažete

557
00:27:01,759 --> 00:27:03,460
[SPEAKER_01] da ćete se vi glavno ženiti,

558
00:27:03,460 --> 00:27:05,599
[SPEAKER_01] a da ćete vašu dječstvo duhovni poziv.

559
00:27:05,599 --> 00:27:06,819
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je jako isto dobra odluka,

560
00:27:06,819 --> 00:27:09,680
[SPEAKER_01] možda budu vaše obitelje isto

561
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:11,119
[SPEAKER_01] pune duhovnih zvanja,

562
00:27:11,119 --> 00:27:13,380
[SPEAKER_01] ako tako čvrsto odlučite,

563
00:27:13,380 --> 00:27:15,500
[SPEAKER_01] pa ćemo joj vidjeti kao kod male Terezije,

564
00:27:15,500 --> 00:27:17,380
[SPEAKER_01] njezini otac je htio biti svečenik,

565
00:27:17,380 --> 00:27:19,480
[SPEAKER_01] pa nekako nije uspio, onda se oženio,

566
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:22,660
[SPEAKER_01] i tako nekako želi uvijek biti svečenik,

567
00:27:22,660 --> 00:27:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] pa iz te silne želje nastroja ta silna duhovnost u obitelji,

568
00:27:26,460 --> 00:27:28,619
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je mala Terezija najbolji predstavnik

569
00:27:28,619 --> 00:27:30,119
[SPEAKER_01] uz njezine ostale sestre.

570
00:27:30,119 --> 00:27:31,859
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je njezina sestra,

571
00:27:31,859 --> 00:27:35,160
[SPEAKER_01] cerina, otišla prije u samostan,

572
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:39,460
[SPEAKER_01] i mala Terezija se s njom nekako susreća.

573
00:27:40,460 --> 00:27:43,519
[SPEAKER_01] Na način da je ova nešto čitala

574
00:27:43,519 --> 00:27:45,740
[SPEAKER_01] i za to nju jako zanimalo.

575
00:27:45,740 --> 00:27:48,079
[SPEAKER_01] Imala jednu bilježnicu

576
00:27:48,079 --> 00:27:51,740
[SPEAKER_01] u kojoj mi je ispisivala citate iz Biblije.

577
00:27:51,740 --> 00:27:55,579
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže ovdje Patre Duda

578
00:27:55,579 --> 00:27:57,039
[SPEAKER_01] da je to bio trenutak

579
00:27:57,039 --> 00:28:00,220
[SPEAKER_01] kada je mala Terezija

580
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:01,980
[SPEAKER_01] otela bilježnicu svoje sestri.

581
00:28:01,980 --> 00:28:03,140
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto dovu še,

582
00:28:03,140 --> 00:28:05,460
[SPEAKER_01] ajde, recimo, ženske znati želje,

583
00:28:05,460 --> 00:28:07,200
[SPEAKER_01] šta se to moja sestra piše,

584
00:28:07,200 --> 00:28:09,200
[SPEAKER_01] ali korisne znati želje

585
00:28:09,200 --> 00:28:12,319
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem je ona prepoznala ljubav Božju

586
00:28:12,319 --> 00:28:14,660
[SPEAKER_01] i ostala zapanjena.

587
00:28:14,660 --> 00:28:19,700
[SPEAKER_01] Naročito se tu od osnovna pjesma nad pjesmama,

588
00:28:19,700 --> 00:28:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] knjiga utjehe proroka Izaije,

589
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:25,039
[SPEAKER_01] razne tekstove.

590
00:28:25,039 --> 00:28:28,079
[SPEAKER_01] Terezija je to upravo istragla iz ruku

591
00:28:28,079 --> 00:28:30,640
[SPEAKER_01] kao iznenada otkriveno blago

592
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:33,920
[SPEAKER_01] i više se od toga nije dala odjeliti.

593
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:36,900
[SPEAKER_01] Tu je našla jezglu svoga maloga puta,

594
00:28:36,900 --> 00:28:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] tekstove koje je toliko puta ponavljala

595
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] u svojim spisima.

596
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:45,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ti su joj tekstovi otvorili vrata

597
00:28:45,319 --> 00:28:47,539
[SPEAKER_01] istraživanju o očinstvu Božje

598
00:28:47,539 --> 00:28:50,700
[SPEAKER_01] i taju je miso rasvjetljavala

599
00:28:50,700 --> 00:28:52,880
[SPEAKER_01] i dala joj zanose dotad

600
00:28:52,880 --> 00:28:55,039
[SPEAKER_01] nepoznate njenom srcu.

601
00:28:55,039 --> 00:28:57,920
[SPEAKER_01] Kroz te tekstove iz bilježnice svoje sestre

602
00:28:57,920 --> 00:29:01,279
[SPEAKER_01] otkrila je ljubav Božju.

603
00:29:02,660 --> 00:29:04,099
[SPEAKER_01] Prevedimo to da nekako na nama

604
00:29:04,099 --> 00:29:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] razumije možda govor.

605
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:08,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ti čite Bibliju.

606
00:29:08,140 --> 00:29:09,380
[SPEAKER_01] Zapisuj.

607
00:29:09,380 --> 00:29:13,839
[SPEAKER_01] Možda je tebi netko otme Bibliju

608
00:29:13,839 --> 00:29:15,400
[SPEAKER_01] ili tu, dakle, tvoju bilježnicu,

609
00:29:15,400 --> 00:29:16,700
[SPEAKER_01] pa se obrati.

610
00:29:16,700 --> 00:29:19,279
[SPEAKER_01] Kao što je bilo kod mala Terezije.

611
00:29:19,279 --> 00:29:21,119
[SPEAKER_01] Otkrije otkriće,

612
00:29:21,119 --> 00:29:24,059
[SPEAKER_01] time što je otela bilježnicu svoje sestri,

613
00:29:24,059 --> 00:29:26,440
[SPEAKER_01] u kojoj je pisala puno ti citata

614
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:27,319
[SPEAKER_01] o Božjoj ljubavi.

615
00:29:27,319 --> 00:29:29,240
[SPEAKER_01] Boga jako domišlja, kao što vidite.

616
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:30,759
[SPEAKER_01] Ima zgodna rješenja.

617
00:29:30,759 --> 00:29:34,460
[SPEAKER_01] Temeljna stvar male Terezije

618
00:29:34,460 --> 00:29:38,460
[SPEAKER_01] bila je svakako njezina slika o tijelu.

619
00:29:38,460 --> 00:29:40,460
[SPEAKER_01] To je opet iz Pavlove poslanice

620
00:29:40,460 --> 00:29:42,339
[SPEAKER_01] korinčanima.

621
00:29:42,339 --> 00:29:44,259
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki ugut ima svoju funkciju.

622
00:29:44,259 --> 00:29:46,559
[SPEAKER_01] Pa onda Terezija razmišljala,

623
00:29:46,559 --> 00:29:48,259
[SPEAKER_01] što će ona biti, što bi se to mogla biti

624
00:29:48,259 --> 00:29:48,900
[SPEAKER_01] u samostanu?

625
00:29:48,900 --> 00:29:50,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ću biti srce.

626
00:29:50,579 --> 00:29:52,960
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo se je nekako najbolji dio izgleda.

627
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:55,460
[SPEAKER_01] Srce kucaje, dakle, on će biti srce.

628
00:29:55,460 --> 00:29:57,940
[SPEAKER_01] Pa će onda ona to, kaže,

629
00:29:57,940 --> 00:29:59,539
[SPEAKER_01] ako srce prestane kucati,

630
00:29:59,539 --> 00:30:01,599
[SPEAKER_01] nema više misionara,

631
00:30:01,599 --> 00:30:03,339
[SPEAKER_01] nema više djevica,

632
00:30:03,339 --> 00:30:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] nema više duhovnih zvanja,

633
00:30:04,960 --> 00:30:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] nema više braćnih parova,

634
00:30:06,480 --> 00:30:07,200
[SPEAKER_01] sve će nestati.

635
00:30:07,200 --> 00:30:10,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ako nema srca, sve će zamrti.

636
00:30:10,099 --> 00:30:13,279
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ću ja u crkvi svoje majici biti srce

637
00:30:13,279 --> 00:30:16,700
[SPEAKER_01] i tako ću biti, nosite veliki blagoslova.

638
00:30:16,700 --> 00:30:18,380
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je Terezija mala,

639
00:30:18,900 --> 00:30:20,980
[SPEAKER_01] koja je bila u samostanu cijeli svoj život,

640
00:30:20,980 --> 00:30:22,400
[SPEAKER_01] kratki život na ovom svijetu,

641
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:23,319
[SPEAKER_01] 24 godine,

642
00:30:23,319 --> 00:30:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] posvetila je i postala je zaštica misionara.

643
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:30,720
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad nije kročila u misije, fizički,

644
00:30:30,720 --> 00:30:34,380
[SPEAKER_01] ali sa srcem je bila sa svim misionarima.

645
00:30:34,380 --> 00:30:36,720
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je crkva prepoznala,

646
00:30:36,720 --> 00:30:38,619
[SPEAKER_01] ne samo kao naučiteljicu crkve,

647
00:30:38,619 --> 00:30:42,640
[SPEAKER_01] nego je prepoznala i kao zašticu misionara.

648
00:30:42,640 --> 00:30:45,259
[SPEAKER_01] Vrlo je zanimljivo ovako iskustvo,

649
00:30:45,259 --> 00:30:47,400
[SPEAKER_01] kako to Bog čudasno čini,

650
00:30:48,039 --> 00:30:51,259
[SPEAKER_01] jer je sa srcem bila sa svakim misionarom.

651
00:30:51,259 --> 00:30:53,900
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, da otkrimo tu duhovnost.

652
00:30:53,900 --> 00:30:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] Nije na odmet,

653
00:30:56,500 --> 00:30:58,339
[SPEAKER_01] ako još niste,

654
00:30:58,339 --> 00:30:59,920
[SPEAKER_01] da se pročitate

655
00:30:59,920 --> 00:31:03,180
[SPEAKER_01] život male Terezije,

656
00:31:03,180 --> 00:31:05,420
[SPEAKER_01] njezinu, dakle, moj život,

657
00:31:05,420 --> 00:31:06,539
[SPEAKER_01] autobiografiju,

658
00:31:06,539 --> 00:31:08,980
[SPEAKER_01] mali put, kako je nazivaju.

659
00:31:08,980 --> 00:31:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tu su mnogi otkrili pravi put duhovnosti.

660
00:31:12,279 --> 00:31:13,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ne nešto veliko.

661
00:31:13,140 --> 00:31:15,680
[SPEAKER_01] Terezija Avilska je velika i snažna,

662
00:31:15,680 --> 00:31:17,920
[SPEAKER_01] ali malo je ljudi išli po njezinom putu.

663
00:31:17,920 --> 00:31:21,079
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je ovako jedno iskustvo.

664
00:31:21,079 --> 00:31:23,339
[SPEAKER_01] Ovdje je možda veći broj ljudi.

665
00:31:23,339 --> 00:31:25,579
[SPEAKER_01] Terezija Avilska je dubinska snažna,

666
00:31:25,579 --> 00:31:27,500
[SPEAKER_01] ali mala Terezija je nekako simpatičnije,

667
00:31:28,240 --> 00:31:29,059
[SPEAKER_01] bliža ljudima.

668
00:31:29,059 --> 00:31:31,579
[SPEAKER_01] Što je prepoznala Terezija u Bibliji?

669
00:31:31,579 --> 00:31:33,700
[SPEAKER_01] Da joj Isus progovara.

670
00:31:33,700 --> 00:31:36,660
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što piše u Bibliji,

671
00:31:36,660 --> 00:31:38,559
[SPEAKER_01] to je kao da Isus njoj govori.

672
00:31:38,559 --> 00:31:39,819
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je doživljavala tu stvar.

673
00:31:39,819 --> 00:31:43,220
[SPEAKER_01] I bile je u trajnoj komunikaciji s njime.

674
00:31:43,220 --> 00:31:46,059
[SPEAKER_01] Zatim,

675
00:31:46,059 --> 00:31:50,940
[SPEAKER_01] to je prenosilo i drugima,

676
00:31:50,940 --> 00:31:52,599
[SPEAKER_01] povijes jedne duše,

677
00:31:52,599 --> 00:31:54,400
[SPEAKER_01] to je taj izdena knjiga koju valja pročitati,

678
00:31:54,400 --> 00:31:56,900
[SPEAKER_01] odgovor Bože milosrđu,

679
00:31:57,500 --> 00:31:58,440
[SPEAKER_01] kako je ona to doživljala,

680
00:31:58,440 --> 00:31:59,240
[SPEAKER_01] na koji način,

681
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:01,359
[SPEAKER_01] po božnom svetom licu,

682
00:32:01,359 --> 00:32:03,700
[SPEAKER_01] prema Izaiji 53.3,

683
00:32:03,700 --> 00:32:05,980
[SPEAKER_01] ono lice koje je izobličeno,

684
00:32:05,980 --> 00:32:07,900
[SPEAKER_01] koje niko više ne časti,

685
00:32:07,900 --> 00:32:09,720
[SPEAKER_01] to je njoj bila motivacija,

686
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:11,319
[SPEAKER_01] zato je ona, Terezija,

687
00:32:11,319 --> 00:32:13,460
[SPEAKER_01] mala od lica Božjega,

688
00:32:13,460 --> 00:32:15,319
[SPEAKER_01] to je jako potreslo,

689
00:32:15,319 --> 00:32:17,240
[SPEAKER_01] od malog Isusa,

690
00:32:17,240 --> 00:32:18,680
[SPEAKER_01] i od lica Božjega,

691
00:32:18,680 --> 00:32:21,759
[SPEAKER_01] Isusova muka i patnje koje on podnosio.

692
00:32:21,759 --> 00:32:23,519
[SPEAKER_01] Sve na temnju te,

693
00:32:23,519 --> 00:32:25,140
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, spoznanje o Božjoj ljubavi.

694
00:32:26,759 --> 00:32:27,500
[SPEAKER_01] I na kraju,

695
00:32:27,500 --> 00:32:29,160
[SPEAKER_01] možda taj dio se zaključiti,

696
00:32:29,160 --> 00:32:31,920
[SPEAKER_01] kako se služala Biblijom,

697
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:34,859
[SPEAKER_01] nastadovala je svetu Ceciliju,

698
00:32:34,859 --> 00:32:36,460
[SPEAKER_01] evanđelje je nosila na srcu,

699
00:32:36,460 --> 00:32:38,539
[SPEAKER_01] to je bila jedna njezdana metoda,

700
00:32:38,539 --> 00:32:40,279
[SPEAKER_01] jedna koja je sjedna na stari,

701
00:32:40,279 --> 00:32:41,299
[SPEAKER_01] novi zavijet,

702
00:32:41,299 --> 00:32:43,039
[SPEAKER_01] molitveno čitanje Biblije,

703
00:32:43,039 --> 00:32:44,660
[SPEAKER_01] takozvana lekcija divina,

704
00:32:44,660 --> 00:32:46,640
[SPEAKER_01] čitaš jedan tekst,

705
00:32:47,519 --> 00:32:48,400
[SPEAKER_01] možda dva puta,

706
00:32:48,400 --> 00:32:48,920
[SPEAKER_01] tri puta,

707
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:49,700
[SPEAKER_01] dok ti ne sjedne,

708
00:32:49,700 --> 00:32:52,039
[SPEAKER_01] i onda moliš na njime.

709
00:32:52,039 --> 00:32:54,559
[SPEAKER_01] Stara metoda čitanja Biblije,

710
00:32:54,559 --> 00:32:55,720
[SPEAKER_01] opet slušanje.

711
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:59,019
[SPEAKER_01] Djavo ne žele da mi slušamo Božju riječ,

712
00:32:59,019 --> 00:33:00,579
[SPEAKER_01] i to ga jako smeta,

713
00:33:00,579 --> 00:33:03,079
[SPEAKER_01] pa će učiniti sve moguće smetnje,

714
00:33:03,079 --> 00:33:04,380
[SPEAKER_01] da tu riječ ne čuješ,

715
00:33:04,380 --> 00:33:07,460
[SPEAKER_01] jer zna koliko imaš blagost o toj riječi.

716
00:33:08,119 --> 00:33:09,359
[SPEAKER_01] Zato evo danas pokušaj

717
00:33:09,359 --> 00:33:11,039
[SPEAKER_01] da ti ne prođe dan,

718
00:33:11,039 --> 00:33:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] da ne slušaš tu riječ,

719
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:16,779
[SPEAKER_01] ili da je ne čitaš kod kuće.

720
00:33:16,779 --> 00:33:19,099
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš i čitati kod kuće,

721
00:33:19,099 --> 00:33:20,460
[SPEAKER_01] i slušati na misi.

722
00:33:20,460 --> 00:33:21,920
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogi od vas, kako čujem,

723
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:23,400
[SPEAKER_01] pripremate se za svetu misu,

724
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:25,500
[SPEAKER_01] tako da čitate riječ Božju prije,

725
00:33:25,500 --> 00:33:26,059
[SPEAKER_01] prekrasno.

726
00:33:26,059 --> 00:33:27,940
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, dolazite na misu,

727
00:33:27,940 --> 00:33:28,460
[SPEAKER_01] pripremljate,

728
00:33:28,460 --> 00:33:29,680
[SPEAKER_01] vi znate koja će riječ biti

729
00:33:29,680 --> 00:33:30,640
[SPEAKER_01] taj dan na svetu misi.

730
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:32,519
[SPEAKER_01] To je idealna stvar.

731
00:33:32,519 --> 00:33:34,359
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, čitaš za sebe,

732
00:33:34,779 --> 00:33:37,140
[SPEAKER_01] na koru razmatraš u uklanjanju u molitvi

733
00:33:37,140 --> 00:33:38,599
[SPEAKER_01] i dođeš na misu,

734
00:33:38,599 --> 00:33:40,819
[SPEAKER_01] to ti je plagoda čista.

735
00:33:40,819 --> 00:33:43,420
[SPEAKER_01] Dobra metoda koju možete svi primijeniti,

736
00:33:43,420 --> 00:33:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] ako želite,

737
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:45,599
[SPEAKER_01] evo ili nekako drugačije,

738
00:33:45,599 --> 00:33:48,319
[SPEAKER_01] da za misuć budeš spreman

739
00:33:48,319 --> 00:33:51,519
[SPEAKER_01] kroz osluškivanje Božje riječi toga dana.

740
00:33:51,519 --> 00:33:53,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ponavljam, moramo puno toga puta

741
00:33:53,619 --> 00:33:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] ponoviti, čitati,

742
00:33:55,420 --> 00:33:57,819
[SPEAKER_01] jer nas džavo jako meta u Božjoj riječi.

743
00:33:57,819 --> 00:34:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] Kad molimo i kad čitamo Božju riječ,

744
00:34:01,099 --> 00:34:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] smetnje su jako velike,

745
00:34:02,380 --> 00:34:04,299
[SPEAKER_01] da ću u zavlja svi potvrditi na svoj način,

746
00:34:04,380 --> 00:34:06,500
[SPEAKER_01] svaki ima svoje smetnje,

747
00:34:06,500 --> 00:34:08,559
[SPEAKER_01] koje to se povezuje s time.

748
00:34:08,559 --> 00:34:11,900
[SPEAKER_01] Poznaje Isus ove šutnje,

749
00:34:11,900 --> 00:34:13,639
[SPEAKER_01] Isus može koji puta i šutiti,

750
00:34:13,639 --> 00:34:15,519
[SPEAKER_01] može progovarati,

751
00:34:15,519 --> 00:34:16,920
[SPEAKER_01] ima razne načine.

752
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:20,059
[SPEAKER_01] Meni se godilo ne jedan put da ne molim za ljude,

753
00:34:20,059 --> 00:34:22,500
[SPEAKER_01] pa imam običaj otvarati Bibliju.

754
00:34:22,500 --> 00:34:24,599
[SPEAKER_01] Otvorim prazna stranica.

755
00:34:24,599 --> 00:34:27,099
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, žao danas Isus nema ništa zaporučiti,

756
00:34:27,099 --> 00:34:28,099
[SPEAKER_01] prazna stranica.

757
00:34:29,039 --> 00:34:31,320
[SPEAKER_01] Šta ćemo sada, tako je moguća isto verzija.

758
00:34:31,320 --> 00:34:34,440
[SPEAKER_01] Da Isus ništa ne progovori, jer on zna kad treba reći,

759
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:37,760
[SPEAKER_01] kad treba šutiti, a naša da poštujemo te stvari.

760
00:34:38,559 --> 00:34:40,639
[SPEAKER_01] I sad pati ljuda zaključio ovo predavanje,

761
00:34:40,639 --> 00:34:42,940
[SPEAKER_01] kaže, mala Terezija otkrila je u Bibliji,

762
00:34:42,940 --> 00:34:44,679
[SPEAKER_01] barem za svoje vrijeme,

763
00:34:44,679 --> 00:34:45,760
[SPEAKER_01] ili barem za se,

764
00:34:45,760 --> 00:34:47,360
[SPEAKER_01] i za tolike duše,

765
00:34:47,360 --> 00:34:49,699
[SPEAKER_01] kojima je poslala učiteljicom,

766
00:34:49,699 --> 00:34:51,500
[SPEAKER_01] novu sliku o Bogu.

767
00:34:51,500 --> 00:34:52,800
[SPEAKER_01] Jako bitno.

768
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:54,440
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je ljubav.

769
00:34:54,440 --> 00:34:56,059
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je otac.

770
00:34:56,059 --> 00:34:57,920
[SPEAKER_01] Iako je sudac,

771
00:34:57,920 --> 00:34:59,460
[SPEAKER_01] nije to sporno u Bibliji,

772
00:34:59,460 --> 00:35:01,059
[SPEAKER_01] ali je i otac.

773
00:35:01,539 --> 00:35:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] Taj dio nije bio otkriven.

774
00:35:02,460 --> 00:35:04,340
[SPEAKER_01] Da je Bog kažnjava,

775
00:35:04,340 --> 00:35:05,760
[SPEAKER_01] da je Bog strogi sudac,

776
00:35:05,760 --> 00:35:07,400
[SPEAKER_01] taj slika je mnogima jasna.

777
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:09,280
[SPEAKER_01] A da je ljubav,

778
00:35:09,280 --> 00:35:10,780
[SPEAKER_01] to treba otkriti.

779
00:35:10,780 --> 00:35:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] To je mala Terezija

780
00:35:12,460 --> 00:35:14,219
[SPEAKER_01] doprinjela toj duhovnosti,

781
00:35:14,219 --> 00:35:15,139
[SPEAKER_01] Boga Otca.

782
00:35:15,139 --> 00:35:17,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je u Bibliji naučila

783
00:35:17,699 --> 00:35:19,099
[SPEAKER_01] i nove kriterije

784
00:35:19,099 --> 00:35:20,980
[SPEAKER_01] za pravi odnos prema Bogu

785
00:35:20,980 --> 00:35:22,460
[SPEAKER_01] u pogledu dobrih dijela.

786
00:35:22,460 --> 00:35:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Činiš dobro dijelo

787
00:35:24,000 --> 00:35:25,480
[SPEAKER_01] sa ljubavlju, sa srcem.

788
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:27,760
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ti to kod Boga vrijedi.

789
00:35:27,760 --> 00:35:29,719
[SPEAKER_01] Makro da praviš jednu malu usjetnicu,

790
00:35:30,739 --> 00:35:32,019
[SPEAKER_01] ali praviš sa srcem,

791
00:35:32,019 --> 00:35:34,900
[SPEAKER_01] onda je to velika stvar.

792
00:35:34,900 --> 00:35:39,239
[SPEAKER_01] To je jedno jako dobro ovako događanje.

793
00:35:39,239 --> 00:35:41,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je pomoću Biblije

794
00:35:41,940 --> 00:35:43,840
[SPEAKER_01] otkrila svoje mjesto u crkvi.

795
00:35:43,840 --> 00:35:46,980
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je njeno otkriće

796
00:35:46,980 --> 00:35:48,340
[SPEAKER_01] značajno u tri smjera.

797
00:35:48,340 --> 00:35:50,559
[SPEAKER_01] Teološkom, antropološkom

798
00:35:50,559 --> 00:35:51,840
[SPEAKER_01] i eklezioškom.

799
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:54,139
[SPEAKER_01] Našla je svoje mjesto prema Bogu,

800
00:35:54,139 --> 00:35:55,519
[SPEAKER_01] prema čovjeku

801
00:35:55,519 --> 00:35:56,539
[SPEAKER_01] i prema crkvi.

802
00:35:56,539 --> 00:35:57,940
[SPEAKER_01] Sve kroz Bibliju

803
00:35:57,940 --> 00:35:59,739
[SPEAKER_01] i upročavanje na taj način

804
00:35:59,739 --> 00:36:00,219
[SPEAKER_01] Boži njih.

805
00:36:00,260 --> 00:36:01,539
[SPEAKER_01] Evo je ovakva zgodna knjižica

806
00:36:01,539 --> 00:36:03,219
[SPEAKER_01] o maloj Tereziji

807
00:36:03,219 --> 00:36:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] i njeđerom otkriću Biblije,

808
00:36:04,739 --> 00:36:06,559
[SPEAKER_01] koja je onda naravno pomogno i nama,

809
00:36:06,559 --> 00:36:09,400
[SPEAKER_01] znači mi živimo u ovim milostnim vremenima,

810
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:11,400
[SPEAKER_01] kada nam je Biblija dostupna

811
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:12,619
[SPEAKER_01] na svakom koraku.

812
00:36:12,619 --> 00:36:15,820
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš kupiti razna izdanja Biblije,

813
00:36:15,820 --> 00:36:17,260
[SPEAKER_01] ovakve i onakve,

814
00:36:17,260 --> 00:36:19,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali bitno je da ju čitaš,

815
00:36:19,159 --> 00:36:20,300
[SPEAKER_01] čitaj, čite.

816
00:36:20,300 --> 00:36:21,260
[SPEAKER_01] Samo budi toj riječi.

817
00:36:21,260 --> 00:36:23,320
[SPEAKER_01] To je riječ Božja.

818
00:36:23,320 --> 00:36:25,420
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je njezina velika snaga

819
00:36:25,420 --> 00:36:27,320
[SPEAKER_01] i njezino značenje.

820
00:36:28,599 --> 00:36:30,579
[SPEAKER_01] Priprava evanđolske objave,

821
00:36:30,579 --> 00:36:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] evo, to sam vam neku način objašnjavo,

822
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:33,679
[SPEAKER_01] stari zavijed,

823
00:36:33,679 --> 00:36:34,480
[SPEAKER_01] Bog priprema,

824
00:36:34,480 --> 00:36:35,880
[SPEAKER_01] Kristo stvaruje.

825
00:36:35,880 --> 00:36:40,460
[SPEAKER_01] Objavu treba prihvatiti vjerom.

826
00:36:42,460 --> 00:36:43,980
[SPEAKER_01] To sam prošlo god da tumačili,

827
00:36:43,980 --> 00:36:44,699
[SPEAKER_01] vjerovanje.

828
00:36:44,699 --> 00:36:46,760
[SPEAKER_01] Bog ti nudi.

829
00:36:46,760 --> 00:36:48,579
[SPEAKER_01] Nudi ti radost,

830
00:36:48,579 --> 00:36:49,980
[SPEAKER_01] ali po križu.

831
00:36:49,980 --> 00:36:52,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ili to prihvaćaš,

832
00:36:52,599 --> 00:36:53,539
[SPEAKER_01] ili ne prihvaćaš.

833
00:36:53,539 --> 00:36:55,400
[SPEAKER_01] Nema nekako kompromisno rješenje.

834
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:57,639
[SPEAKER_01] Želim vjerovati sve više,

835
00:36:57,639 --> 00:37:00,039
[SPEAKER_01] ili ništa ne vjerujem.

836
00:37:00,039 --> 00:37:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] Vjera ne može biti,

837
00:37:02,460 --> 00:37:04,639
[SPEAKER_01] vjeraš od kje se tebi sviđa.

838
00:37:04,639 --> 00:37:06,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ili vjeruješ sve,

839
00:37:06,659 --> 00:37:07,980
[SPEAKER_01] ili ne vjeruješ ništa.

840
00:37:07,980 --> 00:37:09,280
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je to nekako postavljeno.

841
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:10,860
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

842
00:37:10,860 --> 00:37:12,400
[SPEAKER_01] proučavajteš dublje svoju vjeru,

843
00:37:12,460 --> 00:37:14,099
[SPEAKER_01] u njom sve dublje ulaziti.

844
00:37:14,099 --> 00:37:17,239
[SPEAKER_01] Cilje, dakle, toliko jednog događanja.

845
00:37:17,239 --> 00:37:19,099
[SPEAKER_01] Naš odgovor je,

846
00:37:19,099 --> 00:37:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] da, Bože, naš fijat,

847
00:37:21,199 --> 00:37:21,980
[SPEAKER_01] neka mi bude,

848
00:37:21,980 --> 00:37:23,440
[SPEAKER_01] po tvoje riječi.

849
00:37:23,440 --> 00:37:25,119
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je Marija postupila.

850
00:37:25,119 --> 00:37:26,699
[SPEAKER_01] To je naš put,

851
00:37:26,699 --> 00:37:27,780
[SPEAKER_01] to je put svih svetaca.

852
00:37:27,780 --> 00:37:30,699
[SPEAKER_01] Da, što je moguće više do mene,

853
00:37:30,699 --> 00:37:31,860
[SPEAKER_01] kažem, Bože,

854
00:37:31,860 --> 00:37:33,219
[SPEAKER_01] evo, ja ti vjerujem.

855
00:37:33,219 --> 00:37:34,699
[SPEAKER_01] Teško je.

856
00:37:34,699 --> 00:37:36,519
[SPEAKER_01] Boli me koji puta.

857
00:37:36,519 --> 00:37:38,300
[SPEAKER_01] Taj križ nikom nije lagan.

858
00:37:38,300 --> 00:37:40,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sa Petrom kažemo,

859
00:37:40,500 --> 00:37:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] gospodine,

860
00:37:41,599 --> 00:37:42,119
[SPEAKER_01] kamo ćemo.

861
00:37:42,119 --> 00:37:44,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ti imaš riječ iz života vječnog.

862
00:37:44,500 --> 00:37:46,880
[SPEAKER_01] To je Petrov prekrasni odgovor,

863
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:48,199
[SPEAKER_01] koji nas sigurno zadivlje.

864
00:37:48,199 --> 00:37:50,019
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to je prva glava dokumenta.

865
00:37:50,019 --> 00:37:52,059
[SPEAKER_01] Stvarnost objave.

866
00:37:52,059 --> 00:37:53,800
[SPEAKER_01] Objavljene istine.

867
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:55,199
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to su te objavljene istine.

868
00:37:55,199 --> 00:37:56,460
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu pa šprema i previše.

869
00:37:57,239 --> 00:37:58,760
[SPEAKER_01] će iz dovoljnog zapravočavati.

870
00:37:58,760 --> 00:38:00,900
[SPEAKER_01] Koji su sve istine objavljene u Bibliji,

871
00:38:00,900 --> 00:38:03,719
[SPEAKER_01] a crkveni oci na svoj način to prezentirali.

872
00:38:03,719 --> 00:38:05,159
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, imamo sad dalje.

873
00:38:05,159 --> 00:38:06,780
[SPEAKER_01] Drugi dio je

874
00:38:06,780 --> 00:38:08,320
[SPEAKER_01] prenošenje božanske objave.

875
00:38:11,019 --> 00:38:13,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, apostoli su to prvi dobili, tu objavu,

876
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:14,639
[SPEAKER_01] i oni je

877
00:38:14,639 --> 00:38:16,599
[SPEAKER_01] dijele drugima.

878
00:38:16,599 --> 00:38:18,179
[SPEAKER_01] Po polaganju ruku,

879
00:38:18,179 --> 00:38:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] automatski se prenosi

880
00:38:21,199 --> 00:38:22,980
[SPEAKER_01] sve ovlasti, sve milosti,

881
00:38:22,980 --> 00:38:24,360
[SPEAKER_01] koje je Bog dao

882
00:38:24,360 --> 00:38:25,639
[SPEAKER_01] 12 orici apostola.

883
00:38:25,639 --> 00:38:28,059
[SPEAKER_01] To su danas biskupi,

884
00:38:28,059 --> 00:38:30,360
[SPEAKER_01] koji su isto ograničeni ljudi,

885
00:38:30,360 --> 00:38:31,500
[SPEAKER_01] kao nekada i apostoli.

886
00:38:32,639 --> 00:38:34,179
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, imamo 12 apostola,

887
00:38:34,179 --> 00:38:36,179
[SPEAKER_01] svi su se razbježali kod križa,

888
00:38:36,179 --> 00:38:37,400
[SPEAKER_01] zatajili Isusa,

889
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:38,079
[SPEAKER_01] izdali ga.

890
00:38:38,079 --> 00:38:39,760
[SPEAKER_01] Tako i danas.

891
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:41,599
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, imate u crkvi ljude iste,

892
00:38:41,599 --> 00:38:42,739
[SPEAKER_01] imate svete ljude,

893
00:38:42,739 --> 00:38:44,420
[SPEAKER_01] koji ostaju pod križe.

894
00:38:44,420 --> 00:38:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo svete biskupi,

895
00:38:45,880 --> 00:38:46,860
[SPEAKER_01] Evalozija Stepinac,

896
00:38:46,860 --> 00:38:48,639
[SPEAKER_01] jedan od svetih takvih ljudi,

897
00:38:48,639 --> 00:38:50,739
[SPEAKER_01] koji je stajao u svoj narod,

898
00:38:50,739 --> 00:38:51,440
[SPEAKER_01] nije se mico.

899
00:38:51,440 --> 00:38:53,539
[SPEAKER_01] A imate ljude u isto vrijeme,

900
00:38:53,539 --> 00:38:55,599
[SPEAKER_01] znači Evalozija Stepinca,

901
00:38:55,599 --> 00:38:57,639
[SPEAKER_01] koji napuštaju svoje biskupije.

902
00:38:57,639 --> 00:38:59,960
[SPEAKER_01] Papa tadašnji prio 12.

903
00:39:02,099 --> 00:39:03,860
[SPEAKER_01] nije nikome dozvolio

904
00:39:03,860 --> 00:39:05,699
[SPEAKER_01] da ga posjeti,

905
00:39:05,699 --> 00:39:07,360
[SPEAKER_01] ako je napustio svoju biskupiju.

906
00:39:07,360 --> 00:39:08,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ratno je vrijeme,

907
00:39:08,780 --> 00:39:09,599
[SPEAKER_01] drugi svjetski rat,

908
00:39:09,599 --> 00:39:11,679
[SPEAKER_01] mnogi su biskupi napustili svoje biskupije.

909
00:39:11,679 --> 00:39:12,920
[SPEAKER_01] Te biskupe,

910
00:39:12,920 --> 00:39:15,460
[SPEAKER_01] papa pio 12. nije primio audijenciju.

911
00:39:15,460 --> 00:39:16,980
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem,

912
00:39:16,980 --> 00:39:18,679
[SPEAKER_01] vas, vas nemam vremena.

913
00:39:18,679 --> 00:39:20,179
[SPEAKER_01] Jeste napustili svoje stado.

914
00:39:20,179 --> 00:39:21,639
[SPEAKER_01] Niste bilo kaj bili vjerni.

915
00:39:21,639 --> 00:39:23,440
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, papa pio 12.

916
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:24,420
[SPEAKER_01] je malo bio stroki papa,

917
00:39:24,420 --> 00:39:27,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali je to radio po svoje savjesti.

918
00:39:27,159 --> 00:39:29,639
[SPEAKER_01] Jesu napustili stado

919
00:39:29,639 --> 00:39:30,559
[SPEAKER_01] koje im bilo povjereno.

920
00:39:31,559 --> 00:39:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, apostoli su ti koji

921
00:39:32,880 --> 00:39:34,039
[SPEAKER_01] podnose teret.

922
00:39:34,039 --> 00:39:35,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ima svaki apostola,

923
00:39:35,039 --> 00:39:35,800
[SPEAKER_01] dobrih, loši.

924
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:37,139
[SPEAKER_01] To je crkva, dakle.

925
00:39:37,139 --> 00:39:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] Što god čujete da je lošo od crkvi,

926
00:39:38,960 --> 00:39:40,340
[SPEAKER_01] sve vam to je istina.

927
00:39:40,340 --> 00:39:41,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa nije lažno.

928
00:39:41,599 --> 00:39:44,019
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, što god čujete da je dobro od crkvi,

929
00:39:44,019 --> 00:39:44,780
[SPEAKER_01] isto je sve istinito.

930
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,139
[SPEAKER_01] sve to od crkva,

931
00:39:46,139 --> 00:39:48,159
[SPEAKER_01] znači, nemajte se nikad

932
00:39:48,159 --> 00:39:50,420
[SPEAKER_01] voditi tim lošim primjerima.

933
00:39:50,420 --> 00:39:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ima puno svetih, svećenika, divnih ljudi,

934
00:39:52,920 --> 00:39:54,920
[SPEAKER_01] častice star koji žive svoje poslanje,

935
00:39:54,920 --> 00:39:57,059
[SPEAKER_01] a sve negativno također postoji.

936
00:39:57,059 --> 00:39:58,920
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, štao, kao kod Isusa,

937
00:39:58,920 --> 00:40:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] nema razlika.

938
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dobili su vlast.

939
00:40:00,699 --> 00:40:01,940
[SPEAKER_01] Pazite, ljudi, isto dobili vlast.

940
00:40:01,940 --> 00:40:02,980
[SPEAKER_01] Da čini čuda.

941
00:40:04,480 --> 00:40:07,599
[SPEAKER_01] To je stvarnost koja nas, nažalost,

942
00:40:07,599 --> 00:40:09,760
[SPEAKER_01] često kruže s kojom se moramo nositi i boriti,

943
00:40:09,760 --> 00:40:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] ali ona rečenica Isusova,

944
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:13,900
[SPEAKER_01] ni vrata pakla neće nadvarati,

945
00:40:13,900 --> 00:40:17,119
[SPEAKER_01] više puta se pokazala kao stvarna istinita.

946
00:40:17,119 --> 00:40:19,599
[SPEAKER_01] Sad dolazimo do svete predaje.

947
00:40:19,599 --> 00:40:22,239
[SPEAKER_01] Trajno napreduje.

948
00:40:22,239 --> 00:40:23,840
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, neke, ove predaja,

949
00:40:23,840 --> 00:40:27,760
[SPEAKER_01] objašnju sam u kratku kako je nastala Božja riječ.

950
00:40:27,760 --> 00:40:31,460
[SPEAKER_01] To nije, s nema Paolo, pa tu je sad ta Božja riječ.

951
00:40:31,460 --> 00:40:33,639
[SPEAKER_01] Imala svoj nastanak.

952
00:40:34,480 --> 00:40:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan proces.

953
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:37,440
[SPEAKER_01] To je predaja.

954
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:41,340
[SPEAKER_01] Uz predaju ide aktualno crkveno učiteljstvo,

955
00:40:41,340 --> 00:40:44,900
[SPEAKER_01] koji u svoj svojoj slabosti

956
00:40:44,900 --> 00:40:48,460
[SPEAKER_01] proglašavaju ove dogme,

957
00:40:48,460 --> 00:40:50,300
[SPEAKER_01] pa ste ovdje su pisali pape

958
00:40:50,300 --> 00:40:51,579
[SPEAKER_01] koji su bili veliki griješnici,

959
00:40:51,579 --> 00:40:55,320
[SPEAKER_01] ali nisu pisali ništa kontra vjere.

960
00:40:55,320 --> 00:40:56,300
[SPEAKER_01] To je interesantno.

961
00:40:56,300 --> 00:40:58,179
[SPEAKER_01] Kao što, recimo,

962
00:40:58,179 --> 00:41:02,039
[SPEAKER_01] djeca kod ukazanja u Lurdu i Fatimi

963
00:41:02,039 --> 00:41:04,500
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu ništa progovoriti

964
00:41:04,500 --> 00:41:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] što im nije dano.

965
00:41:06,480 --> 00:41:09,900
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su par puta pokušali nešto reći,

966
00:41:09,900 --> 00:41:11,719
[SPEAKER_01] ali ništa, nije išlo.

967
00:41:11,719 --> 00:41:13,579
[SPEAKER_01] Tako isto, dakle,

968
00:41:13,579 --> 00:41:15,320
[SPEAKER_01] i učiteljstvo crkve

969
00:41:15,320 --> 00:41:18,380
[SPEAKER_01] nikada ne može raditi nešto kontra vjere.

970
00:41:19,739 --> 00:41:22,239
[SPEAKER_01] bio je najgori papa u povijesti crkve Aleksandar VI,

971
00:41:22,239 --> 00:41:23,159
[SPEAKER_01] zvani Borđija,

972
00:41:23,159 --> 00:41:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] koji je živio vrlo nemoralno,

973
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:30,260
[SPEAKER_01] ali jednu dogmu nije donio protiv crkve.

974
00:41:30,260 --> 00:41:32,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, na dogme strogi nauk,

975
00:41:32,480 --> 00:41:33,199
[SPEAKER_01] koji se ne mijenja.

976
00:41:33,199 --> 00:41:34,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo što je ovdje,

977
00:41:34,780 --> 00:41:36,119
[SPEAKER_01] to se neće nikad mijenjati,

978
00:41:36,119 --> 00:41:37,019
[SPEAKER_01] jer to je nauk crkve,

979
00:41:37,019 --> 00:41:37,800
[SPEAKER_01] to je ta predaja.

980
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:41,340
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, on nikakvu dogmu nije donio kontra crkve,

981
00:41:41,340 --> 00:41:42,300
[SPEAKER_01] a žive jako loše.

982
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:44,360
[SPEAKER_01] Kako je to Isus riješio?

983
00:41:44,360 --> 00:41:45,219
[SPEAKER_01] Ono rečenicom,

984
00:41:45,219 --> 00:41:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] slušajte što vam kažu,

985
00:41:47,380 --> 00:41:49,579
[SPEAKER_01] a nemojte čini što oni čine.

986
00:41:49,579 --> 00:41:52,679
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, u šteljstvo crkve ti uvijek kaže

987
00:41:52,679 --> 00:41:54,760
[SPEAKER_01] dobar put, živi tako.

988
00:41:54,760 --> 00:41:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] To ti je jako dobro.

989
00:41:56,500 --> 00:42:00,840
[SPEAKER_01] A možeš sresti vrlo loše svečenike,

990
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:02,659
[SPEAKER_01] duhovne ljude koji te sablazna.

991
00:42:02,659 --> 00:42:04,619
[SPEAKER_01] To je moguće.

992
00:42:04,619 --> 00:42:06,960
[SPEAKER_01] Nemoj živjeti kako oni žive.

993
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:09,159
[SPEAKER_01] Žive onako ako ti oni govore.

994
00:42:09,159 --> 00:42:10,199
[SPEAKER_01] To je Isus opravilo.

995
00:42:10,199 --> 00:42:11,579
[SPEAKER_01] Vrlo jednostavno, vrlo jasno.

996
00:42:12,199 --> 00:42:13,559
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ćemo ići naprijed?

997
00:42:13,559 --> 00:42:17,360
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ta povezanost između pisma,

998
00:42:17,360 --> 00:42:20,579
[SPEAKER_01] predaje i učiteljstva crkve.

999
00:42:20,579 --> 00:42:22,599
[SPEAKER_01] Velika poveznica,

1000
00:42:22,599 --> 00:42:24,940
[SPEAKER_01] o čemu govore o ovih par točaka,

1001
00:42:24,940 --> 00:42:25,900
[SPEAKER_01] 8, 9 i 10.

1002
00:42:25,900 --> 00:42:28,199
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, moramo čitati pismo,

1003
00:42:28,199 --> 00:42:31,539
[SPEAKER_01] moramo čitati dokumente crkve

1004
00:42:31,539 --> 00:42:34,980
[SPEAKER_01] iz te predaje

1005
00:42:34,980 --> 00:42:37,599
[SPEAKER_01] i moramo sluškivati sadašnji trenutak.

1006
00:42:37,599 --> 00:42:41,320
[SPEAKER_01] Primjerice socijalne dokumente crkve,

1007
00:42:41,320 --> 00:42:44,340
[SPEAKER_01] kada je papa Love 13 izdao prvu encikliku

1008
00:42:44,340 --> 00:42:48,019
[SPEAKER_01] Relubnovarum 1821. godine,

1009
00:42:48,019 --> 00:42:51,659
[SPEAKER_01] od tad svakih deseta godina

1010
00:42:51,659 --> 00:42:53,679
[SPEAKER_01] pape izdaju novu encikliku.

1011
00:42:53,679 --> 00:42:56,219
[SPEAKER_01] Jesi menja situaciju u svijetu,

1012
00:42:56,219 --> 00:42:58,900
[SPEAKER_01] politički, dakle društvena, ekonomska,

1013
00:42:58,900 --> 00:43:01,579
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda papa s nove strane gleda na te stvari,

1014
00:43:02,019 --> 00:43:05,300
[SPEAKER_01] to su socijalne promjene u društvu koje je kao takve moguće.

1015
00:43:05,360 --> 00:43:07,780
[SPEAKER_01] Moramo to iščitavati, vidjeti gdje je s koji je sad trenutak,

1016
00:43:07,780 --> 00:43:09,739
[SPEAKER_01] što sta crkvenočitejstvo govori.

1017
00:43:09,739 --> 00:43:14,300
[SPEAKER_01] Pa uz Bibliju imate stotinu dokumenta crkvenih

1018
00:43:14,300 --> 00:43:17,019
[SPEAKER_01] od ovih gdje je verbum, papirnih dokumenta,

1019
00:43:17,019 --> 00:43:18,559
[SPEAKER_01] pa ono što vas interesira,

1020
00:43:18,559 --> 00:43:20,800
[SPEAKER_01] malo ubaciti u svoj program.

1021
00:43:21,300 --> 00:43:23,219
[SPEAKER_01] Oni koji vode druge kroz programe,

1022
00:43:23,219 --> 00:43:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] nije loše malo ubaciti neki dokumenta crkve,

1023
00:43:26,000 --> 00:43:28,219
[SPEAKER_01] to su male knjižice, nisu velike,

1024
00:43:28,219 --> 00:43:29,780
[SPEAKER_01] ali su jako bremenite i snažne,

1025
00:43:29,780 --> 00:43:32,199
[SPEAKER_01] da se malo i ti dokumenti pročitaju,

1026
00:43:32,199 --> 00:43:34,559
[SPEAKER_01] pa da budemo u toku, ne možemo sve,

1027
00:43:34,559 --> 00:43:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] jer to je preveliko da će događanje,

1028
00:43:36,659 --> 00:43:38,800
[SPEAKER_01] ali barem neki dokumenta vidjeti

1029
00:43:38,800 --> 00:43:40,719
[SPEAKER_01] kako to se crkva naučava,

1030
00:43:40,719 --> 00:43:41,780
[SPEAKER_01] što se to na tu govori

1031
00:43:41,780 --> 00:43:44,480
[SPEAKER_01] za ovaj naš tadašnji trenutak.

1032
00:43:44,480 --> 00:43:46,039
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, idemo dalje.

1033
00:43:46,039 --> 00:43:50,659
[SPEAKER_01] Najpoznatiji psalam koji govori

1034
00:43:50,659 --> 00:43:53,219
[SPEAKER_01] o Božjoj riječi je psalam 119.

1035
00:43:53,219 --> 00:43:57,139
[SPEAKER_01] On je najduži psalam,

1036
00:43:57,139 --> 00:44:01,139
[SPEAKER_01] a govori upravo o pohvali Božjoj riječi.

1037
00:44:01,139 --> 00:44:03,760
[SPEAKER_01] Nije loše da ga se ga pročitate,

1038
00:44:03,760 --> 00:44:05,739
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo joj pokušali malo izdvojiti

1039
00:44:05,739 --> 00:44:08,239
[SPEAKER_01] neke od tih citata,

1040
00:44:08,239 --> 00:44:09,739
[SPEAKER_01] znači 119.

1041
00:44:09,739 --> 00:44:13,739
[SPEAKER_01] Kako će mladić čistin sačuvati svoj put

1042
00:44:13,739 --> 00:44:15,760
[SPEAKER_01] slušajući tvoju riječi,

1043
00:44:15,760 --> 00:44:17,300
[SPEAKER_01] znači predlagođuje se tvojoj riječi.

1044
00:44:17,300 --> 00:44:19,239
[SPEAKER_01] To je deveti redak.

1045
00:44:20,019 --> 00:44:22,480
[SPEAKER_01] evo, ciljna riječi koja živete biti

1046
00:44:22,480 --> 00:44:23,480
[SPEAKER_01] na Božjom putu,

1047
00:44:23,480 --> 00:44:25,079
[SPEAKER_01] čitajte Božju riječ.

1048
00:44:25,079 --> 00:44:26,280
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ćeš sačuvati svoj put?

1049
00:44:26,280 --> 00:44:28,679
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da čitaš Božju riječ.

1050
00:44:28,679 --> 00:44:30,280
[SPEAKER_01] Može biti dostanje i pravilo.

1051
00:44:30,280 --> 00:44:32,340
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo će biti sve objašnjeno

1052
00:44:32,340 --> 00:44:33,460
[SPEAKER_01] kako živjeti.

1053
00:44:34,579 --> 00:44:35,199
[SPEAKER_01] dalje.

1054
00:44:35,199 --> 00:44:38,539
[SPEAKER_01] Uzeli smo ovu sliku malo o Marije Magdalene,

1055
00:44:38,539 --> 00:44:40,639
[SPEAKER_01] 25.32,

1056
00:44:40,639 --> 00:44:43,320
[SPEAKER_01] gdje se puno toga govori

1057
00:44:43,320 --> 00:44:46,659
[SPEAKER_01] kako je ona i u prašini bila.

1058
00:44:46,659 --> 00:44:49,159
[SPEAKER_01] Znate da je Isus oslobodio

1059
00:44:49,159 --> 00:44:50,099
[SPEAKER_01] obtužnice,

1060
00:44:50,099 --> 00:44:51,980
[SPEAKER_01] pa je podigao,

1061
00:44:51,980 --> 00:44:54,440
[SPEAKER_01] evo, to imamo 25.32.

1062
00:44:54,440 --> 00:45:17,760
[SPEAKER_01] Moja duša leži u prašini,

1063
00:45:18,099 --> 00:45:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] po riječi svoj vrati mi život.

1064
00:45:19,960 --> 00:45:28,739
[SPEAKER_01] Kazivao sam ti svoje putove

1065
00:45:28,739 --> 00:45:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] i ti si me čuo.

1066
00:45:29,960 --> 00:45:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pravilima me svojim nauči.

1067
00:45:32,559 --> 00:45:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] Pokaži mi put odredaba svojih

1068
00:45:35,500 --> 00:45:37,699
[SPEAKER_00] i o čudesima ću tvojim razmišljati.

1069
00:45:37,699 --> 00:45:40,639
[SPEAKER_00] Suzer oni duša moja od žalosti.

1070
00:45:40,639 --> 00:45:42,059
[SPEAKER_01] Po tradiciji,

1071
00:45:42,059 --> 00:45:43,820
[SPEAKER_01] ona žena koja je pravila Isusu noge

1072
00:45:43,820 --> 00:45:44,559
[SPEAKER_01] sa suzama,

1073
00:45:44,559 --> 00:45:45,559
[SPEAKER_01] brisala kosom,

1074
00:45:45,559 --> 00:45:47,159
[SPEAKER_01] znači nakon ga nuća,

1075
00:45:47,239 --> 00:45:48,400
[SPEAKER_01] što je doživa susret s njime.

1076
00:45:48,400 --> 00:45:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] Kada je onda rekao na černicu

1077
00:45:50,119 --> 00:45:51,480
[SPEAKER_01] tko je od vas bez grijeha,

1078
00:45:51,480 --> 00:45:53,699
[SPEAKER_01] neka prvi baci kame na nju,

1079
00:45:53,699 --> 00:45:54,320
[SPEAKER_01] ona je doživjela

1080
00:45:54,320 --> 00:45:55,820
[SPEAKER_01] svoju veliku milost sa Isusem.

1081
00:45:55,820 --> 00:46:01,840
[SPEAKER_00] Po riječi svoj time podigni.

1082
00:46:01,840 --> 00:46:04,239
[SPEAKER_01] Isus je rekao

1083
00:46:04,239 --> 00:46:05,739
[SPEAKER_01] tko je od vas bez grijeha,

1084
00:46:05,739 --> 00:46:07,960
[SPEAKER_01] neka prvi baci kame na nju.

1085
00:46:07,960 --> 00:46:09,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ti su se razbježali.

1086
00:46:09,380 --> 00:46:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda Isus pita,

1087
00:46:11,000 --> 00:46:11,980
[SPEAKER_01] gdje su tvoji dužitelji?

1088
00:46:11,980 --> 00:46:12,579
[SPEAKER_01] Nikog nema.

1089
00:46:12,579 --> 00:46:15,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ni ja te ne osuđujem.

1090
00:46:15,159 --> 00:46:16,659
[SPEAKER_01] To je Isusa na černica,

1091
00:46:16,800 --> 00:46:17,599
[SPEAKER_01] tu je Marija doživjela

1092
00:46:17,599 --> 00:46:18,840
[SPEAKER_01] preporod svoje duše.

1093
00:46:18,840 --> 00:46:21,139
[SPEAKER_01] Jedin koji je mogo baci kame na nju

1094
00:46:21,139 --> 00:46:21,800
[SPEAKER_01] bio je Isus.

1095
00:46:21,800 --> 00:46:23,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ali on ne baca.

1096
00:46:23,360 --> 00:46:24,840
[SPEAKER_01] To je to silna ljubav.

1097
00:46:24,840 --> 00:46:26,519
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je onda odlučio

1098
00:46:26,519 --> 00:46:27,099
[SPEAKER_01] da biti uz njega,

1099
00:46:27,099 --> 00:46:27,760
[SPEAKER_01] što će drugi zove.

1100
00:46:33,800 --> 00:46:44,880
[SPEAKER_01] Daleko me drži od puta zablude

1101
00:46:44,880 --> 00:46:46,860
[SPEAKER_00] i zakonome svojim obdari.

1102
00:46:46,860 --> 00:46:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] Put istine ja sam odabrao.

1103
00:46:49,500 --> 00:46:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] Pred oči sam stavio odluke tvoje.

1104
00:46:51,900 --> 00:46:55,099
[SPEAKER_00] Uz probi se tvoje ja čvrsto prijanjam.

1105
00:46:55,099 --> 00:46:57,460
[SPEAKER_00] O Jahve nemoj me postidjeti.

1106
00:46:58,199 --> 00:47:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kročim putem zapovjedi tvojih,

1107
00:47:01,000 --> 00:47:02,659
[SPEAKER_00] jer si mi prosvijetlio srce.

1108
00:47:03,659 --> 00:47:04,880
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je bari Magdalena.

1109
00:47:04,880 --> 00:47:05,320
[SPEAKER_01] Malo vidite,

1110
00:47:05,320 --> 00:47:06,460
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je nakon sluča.

1111
00:47:06,460 --> 00:47:07,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ona Isusa hvata,

1112
00:47:07,820 --> 00:47:08,500
[SPEAKER_01] ali on kaže

1113
00:47:08,500 --> 00:47:09,139
[SPEAKER_01] čekaj, čekaj sad,

1114
00:47:09,139 --> 00:47:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] još nisi uskrsnula.

1115
00:47:10,539 --> 00:47:12,139
[SPEAKER_01] Malo pričekaj, dakle.

1116
00:47:12,139 --> 00:47:14,159
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ćemo se onda družiti,

1117
00:47:14,159 --> 00:47:16,360
[SPEAKER_01] jer tu sliku namjeno izabrli,

1118
00:47:16,360 --> 00:47:17,920
[SPEAKER_01] jer ona ga prva vidi

1119
00:47:17,920 --> 00:47:19,500
[SPEAKER_01] nakon sluča,

1120
00:47:19,500 --> 00:47:21,019
[SPEAKER_01] jer ga je žarko tražila.

1121
00:47:21,019 --> 00:47:22,820
[SPEAKER_01] Tražila ga cijelim svojim bićem.

1122
00:47:22,820 --> 00:47:23,579
[SPEAKER_01] Srce ga je tražila.

1123
00:47:23,579 --> 00:47:24,199
[SPEAKER_01] Srce je bitno.

1124
00:47:24,739 --> 00:47:26,360
[SPEAKER_01] Da srce bude u toj riječi,

1125
00:47:26,360 --> 00:47:27,780
[SPEAKER_01] da ga doželjavamo

1126
00:47:27,780 --> 00:47:28,699
[SPEAKER_01] i Bog je dao milost

1127
00:47:28,699 --> 00:47:29,840
[SPEAKER_01] da ga prva ona vidi

1128
00:47:29,840 --> 00:47:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] nakon sluča.

1129
00:47:31,039 --> 00:47:31,639
[SPEAKER_01] A to je,

1130
00:47:31,639 --> 00:47:33,599
[SPEAKER_01] Božja pedagoge je uvijek zanimljiva.

1131
00:47:33,599 --> 00:47:35,480
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, možemo dalje.

1132
00:47:35,480 --> 00:47:39,400
[SPEAKER_01] Epsalam 119,

1133
00:47:39,400 --> 00:47:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] isto, 105. redak.

1134
00:47:41,079 --> 00:47:43,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ona da je riječ tvoja,

1135
00:47:43,780 --> 00:47:44,960
[SPEAKER_01] nozi moja, je svjetljka.

1136
00:47:44,960 --> 00:47:47,400
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ideš po mraku,

1137
00:47:47,400 --> 00:47:48,860
[SPEAKER_01] živiš u svijetu,

1138
00:47:48,860 --> 00:47:50,059
[SPEAKER_01] koji je jako mračan.

1139
00:47:50,059 --> 00:47:51,960
[SPEAKER_01] Uzmeš Božju riječ,

1140
00:47:51,960 --> 00:47:52,900
[SPEAKER_01] ona ti je svjetljka.

1141
00:47:53,719 --> 00:47:54,920
[SPEAKER_01] Pa vidiš gdje ćeš kročiti.

1142
00:47:54,920 --> 00:47:57,059
[SPEAKER_01] Taj riječ mnogi ljudi obratila,

1143
00:47:57,059 --> 00:47:58,619
[SPEAKER_01] mnogi dola na pravi put,

1144
00:47:58,619 --> 00:48:00,840
[SPEAKER_01] jer su uzeli tu riječ Božju

1145
00:48:00,840 --> 00:48:01,760
[SPEAKER_01] u svoje ruke,

1146
00:48:01,760 --> 00:48:03,860
[SPEAKER_01] s njom su si osvjetljali put.

1147
00:48:03,860 --> 00:48:04,300
[SPEAKER_01] Pa evo,

1148
00:48:04,300 --> 00:48:07,440
