00:53:27,000 --> 00:53:29,059
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže Isu,

1357
00:53:29,059 --> 00:53:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] dostaje svakom danu

1358
00:53:29,960 --> 00:53:30,579
[SPEAKER_01] njegovog zla.

1359
00:53:30,579 --> 00:53:32,480
[SPEAKER_01] Današnji dan živi

1360
00:53:32,480 --> 00:53:33,860
[SPEAKER_01] s povjerenjem u Boga,

1361
00:53:33,860 --> 00:53:35,179
[SPEAKER_01] nosi svoj križ,

1362
00:53:35,179 --> 00:53:36,059
[SPEAKER_01] idi za Isusom.

1363
00:53:36,059 --> 00:53:36,920
[SPEAKER_01] Sve su rečenice

1364
00:53:36,920 --> 00:53:38,079
[SPEAKER_01] koje jako dobro znamo

1365
00:53:38,079 --> 00:53:39,840
[SPEAKER_01] i tako iz dana u dan.

1366
00:53:39,840 --> 00:53:41,840
[SPEAKER_01] On će ti Bog otkrivati

1367
00:53:41,840 --> 00:53:43,300
[SPEAKER_01] sve veće milosti,

1368
00:53:43,300 --> 00:53:44,079
[SPEAKER_01] radosti,

1369
00:53:44,079 --> 00:53:45,800
[SPEAKER_01] događaje.

1370
00:53:45,800 --> 00:53:46,460
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, evo,

1371
00:53:46,460 --> 00:53:47,420
[SPEAKER_01] mi zaista u zajednici

1372
00:53:47,420 --> 00:53:48,139
[SPEAKER_01] možemo posvjedočiti

1373
00:53:48,139 --> 00:53:48,780
[SPEAKER_01] mnoge milosti

1374
00:53:48,780 --> 00:53:49,659
[SPEAKER_01] koje se događaju

1375
00:53:49,659 --> 00:53:50,980
[SPEAKER_01] upravo na taj način.

1376
00:53:50,980 --> 00:53:53,079
[SPEAKER_01] Osluškuje se Božja riječ,

1377
00:53:53,079 --> 00:53:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] mnogi su u molitvi,

1378
00:53:54,699 --> 00:53:56,019
[SPEAKER_01] pa nam Boga napreda

1379
00:53:56,019 --> 00:53:56,599
[SPEAKER_01] daje, spoznaje

1380
00:53:56,599 --> 00:53:58,079
[SPEAKER_01] kako će neke stvari izgledati,

1381
00:53:58,079 --> 00:53:59,659
[SPEAKER_01] dobijemo viziju

1382
00:53:59,659 --> 00:54:00,440
[SPEAKER_01] nekog događaja,

1383
00:54:00,440 --> 00:54:02,139
[SPEAKER_01] pogotovo neki važni događaja,

1384
00:54:02,139 --> 00:54:03,860
[SPEAKER_01] upozore nas čak

1385
00:54:03,860 --> 00:54:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] na neke nesreće

1386
00:54:04,739 --> 00:54:05,780
[SPEAKER_01] koje možemo izbjeći.

1387
00:54:05,780 --> 00:54:08,179
[SPEAKER_01] Boga ti napred sve pokaže,

1388
00:54:08,179 --> 00:54:10,260
[SPEAKER_01] on ti ide tim putem,

1389
00:54:10,260 --> 00:54:11,219
[SPEAKER_01] jer on je psalam,

1390
00:54:11,219 --> 00:54:13,139
[SPEAKER_01] pa da mi dolinom smrti proći,

1391
00:54:13,139 --> 00:54:14,019
[SPEAKER_01] zla se ne bojim,

1392
00:54:14,019 --> 00:54:15,199
[SPEAKER_01] jer ti si sa mnom.

1393
00:54:15,199 --> 00:54:17,039
[SPEAKER_01] To je iskustvo vjernika

1394
00:54:17,039 --> 00:54:18,800
[SPEAKER_01] koji osluškuje Božju riječ,

1395
00:54:18,800 --> 00:54:19,679
[SPEAKER_01] koji po njoj živi,

1396
00:54:19,679 --> 00:54:21,699
[SPEAKER_01] on može ići dolinom smrti,

1397
00:54:21,699 --> 00:54:23,219
[SPEAKER_01] mičak se ne boji,

1398
00:54:23,219 --> 00:54:24,260
[SPEAKER_01] a zna da je Bog s njime.

1399
00:54:24,260 --> 00:54:26,159
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to je jedno veliko iskustvo,

1400
00:54:26,159 --> 00:54:27,360
[SPEAKER_01] želim da svi zajedno

1401
00:54:27,360 --> 00:54:29,139
[SPEAKER_01] osjećamo kroz ovo razmišljanje

1402
00:54:29,139 --> 00:54:30,920
[SPEAKER_01] o Božjoj riječi,

1403
